ng%20of%20the%20yen%20carry%20trade%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%20spooked%20markets%20as%20investors%20sold%20off%20their%20positions%2C%20including%20in%20the%20US%20market%2C%20to%20cover%20their%20Japanese%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20from%20where%20we%20started%20a%20month%20ago%20to%20where%20we%20are%20now%2C%20the%20deleveraging%20of%20the%20yen%20has%20pretty%20much%20played%20out%2C%20says%20Jayati%20Bharadwaj%2C%20a%20global%20FX%20strategist%20at%20TD%20Securities.%20It%20may%20continue%20in%20the%20background%2C%20but%20an%20unwinding%20risk%20that%20could%20further%20trickle%20into%20the%20global%20market%20is%20much%20lower%20now%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20currency%20traders%20should%20be%20on%20guard.%20Cooling%20global%20growth%2C%20continued%20geopolitical%20risks%2C%20and%20uncertainty%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trade-vs-kamala-harris-opportunity-economy-policies-market-impact-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20election%20outcomes%3C%2Fa%3E%20mean%20it%20could%20be%20a%20choppy%20ride%20for%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20it's%20still%20possible%20that%20other%20carry%20trades%20unwind%2C%20which%20happens%20when%20traders%20borrow%20in%20a%20currency%20with%20low%20interest%20rates%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20higher-rate%20one%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20moves%20sharply.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20Mexican%20peso%20could%20see%20a%20violent%20drop%20in%20value%20as%20the%20country%20takes%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-analysis-india-narendra-modi-mexico-claudia-sheinbaum-volatility-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20leadership%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20create%20uncertainty%20around%20central%20bank%20policies.%20Until%20now%2C%20peso%20investors%20have%20enjoyed%20interest%20rates%20ranging%20between%2010.75%25%20to%2011%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20carry%20unwinds%20are%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20story%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20where%20the%20real%20risk%20in%20FX%20markets%20is%20right%20now%2C%20says%20Bharadwaj.%20The%20next%20shoe%20to%20drop%20will%20be%20triggered%20by%20a%20slowdown%20of%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20which%20could%20reshuffle%20values%20in%20the%20currencies%20of%20the%20big%20global%20players%2C%20she%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20is%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world's%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Bharadwaj%20said.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20markets%20feel%20that%20the%20US%20is%20weak%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20is%20still%20holding%20up%2C%20and%20that's%20why%2C%20at%20times%2C%20you've%20seen%20global%20equities%20markets%20rallying%20and%20holding%20up.%20I%20think%20if%20you%20start%20getting%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20data%20coming%20in%20much%20weaker%20than%20expected%2C%20such%20that%20attention%20shifts%20from%20the%20US%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20China%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20markets%20will%20get%20really%20concerned%20about%20global%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FBlogs%2FArticles%2F2024%2F07%2F16%2Fglobal-growth-steady-amid-slowing-disinflation-and-rising-policy-uncertainty%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20global%20economy's%20main%20growth%20engines%2C%20China%20and%20India%2C%20are%20set%20to%20slow%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20The%20World%20Bank's%20deputy%20chief%20economist%20said%20that%20although%20global%20growth%20is%20stabilizing%20post-COVID%2C%2060%25%20of%20the%20world's%20economies%20will%20advance%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F06%2F11%2Fglobal-growth-economic-prospects-expert-answers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslower%20pace%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20their%20pre-pandemic%20average%20through%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20an%20IMF%20chart%20showing%20projected%20output%20gaps%20by%20region.%20This%20measure%20of%20efficiency%20is%20based%20on%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20country's%20actual%20output%20and%20its%20output%20capacity%2C%20measured%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20its%20potential%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22790%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20demonstrating%20US%20outpacing%20Europe%20and%20China%20in%20output%20efficiency.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8fe20c72ebc54a40e8fb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22924%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EIMF%2C%20World%20Economic%20Outlook%3B%20and%20IMF%20staff%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20global%20GDP%20%E2%80%94%20excluding%20the%20US%E2%80%94%20or%20survey%20data%20signals%20a%20slowdown%20is%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20then%20the%20European%20currency%20market%20would%20be%20facing%20elevated%20risk.%20The%20euro%20at%20%241.11%20and%20the%20pound%20at%20%241.31%20versus%20the%20dollar%20are%20running%20hot%20and%20at%20their%20highest%20prices%20in%20over%20a%20year.%20Simply%20put%2C%20they're%20too%20optimistically%20priced%2C%20Bharadwaj%20noted.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20dollar's%20positioning%20relative%20to%20both%20currencies%20looks%20more%20neutral%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpectations%20of%20a%20weaker%20dollar%20have%20fueled%20bullish%20sentiment%20toward%20the%20euro%20and%20pound.%20As%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20prepares%20to%20make%20its%20first%20round%20of%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20of%20this%20cycle%2C%20demand%20for%20the%20dollar%20would%20drop%20as%20investors%20hunt%20for%20returns%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20US%20economic%20data%20stabilizes%20while%20global%20growth%20slows%2C%20as%20Bharadwaj%20expects%2C%20European%20currencies%20could%20be%20set%20for%20a%20violent%20snapback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cata