0sugar%20levels.%20A%20sensor%2C%20inserted%20just%20under%20the%20skin%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Evia%20a%20tiny%20needle%2C%20measures%20the%20glucose%20(sugar)%20in%20the%20fluid%20around%20the%20cells%2C%20and%20provides%20ongoing%20updates%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20you%20needed%20a%20prescription%20to%20get%20one.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fpress-announcements%2Ffda-clears-first-over-counter-continuous-glucose-monitor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%20approved%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20over-the-counter%20in%20March.%20Companies%20can%20now%20market%20CGMs%20to%20anyone%2C%20no%20prescription%20necessary%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20the%20100%20million%20Americans%20with%20prediabetes%2C%20or%20any%20of%20the%20other%20200%20million%20adults%20who%20want%20to%20harness%20their%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20as%20more%20people%20seek%20personalized%20solutions%20to%20optimize%20their%20bodies%2C%20the%20market%20for%20CGMs%20has%20skyrocketed.%20It%20is%20projected%20to%20more%20than%20double%20from%20an%20estimated%20value%20of%20%246.8%20billion%20in%202023%20to%20%2420.2%20billion%20in%202032%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gminsights.com%2Findustry-analysis%2Fcontinuous-glucose-monitoring-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Market%20Insights%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacobs%20said%20a%20CGM%2C%20recommended%20by%20a%20fellow%20athlete%2C%20was%20a%20game%20changer.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20track%20how%20her%20body%20was%20responding%20to%20food%2C%20and%20use%20that%20data%20to%20perfect%20her%20training%20and%20performance.%20It%20was%20like%20tracking%20her%20heart%20rate%20or%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eknowing%20her%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvo2-max-explained-what-is-good-how-improve-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVO2%20max%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20It%20gave%20her%20a%20clearer%20insight%20into%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20her%20body%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20a%20sports%20dietitian%2C%20Jacobs%20started%20tapping%20into%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarbs-heart-health-key-for-nutrition-wholegrain-over-processed-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplex%20carbs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eating%20more%2C%20and%20eating%20earlier%20so%20she%20could%20have%20lasting%20energy.%20Her%20fatigue%20vanished.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20three%20hours%20of%20riding%2C%20I%20had%20a%20ton%20of%20energy%2C%20power%20in%20my%20muscles%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20feel%20spikes%20of%20being%20up%20and%20crashing%2C%20I%20was%20just%20able%20to%20last%20longer%2C%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacobs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c1e9c0e-43c2-4063-a267-2c3f621ef37b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20does%20blood%20sugar%20matter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fnormal-blood-sugar-levels%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20sugar%20level%3C%2Fa%3E%20measures%20how%20much%20glucose%20is%20in%20your%20blood%2C%20which%20comes%20from%20breaking%20down%20carbohydrates%20you%20eat%20for%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalancing%20blood%20sugar%20is%20crucial%20for%20people%20with%20diabetes%2C%20who%20can%20face%20life-threatening%20consequences%20if%20their%20levels%20drop%20too%20low%20or%20spike%20too%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20wellness%20companies%20like%20Levels%20and%20Nutrisense%20increasingly%20argue%20that%20blood%20sugar%20is%20an%20important%20metric%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20diabetes%2C%20since%20it%20ties%20into%20holistic%20lifestyle%20factors%20ranging%20from%20diet%20to%20sleep%20to%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20various%20health%20tech%20products%2C%20these%20companies%20aim%20to%20offer%20consumers%20more%20insight%20into%20how%20their%20daily%20habits%20affect%20their%20blood%20sugar%2C%20and%20help%20them%20analyze%20patterns%20to%20land%20on%20what%20behaviors%20can%20help%20them%20feel%20and%20perform%20their%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnderstanding%20your%20glucose%20patterns%20is%20like%20having%20an%20MRI%20on%20how%20all%20the%20sort%20of%20holistic%20features%20of%20your%20daily%20choices%20are%20working%20together%20to%20generate%20metabolic%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Casey%20Means%2C%20co-founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstreaklinks.com%2FB8xIVnzQkFEIoTQaKgdUxVrv%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.levelshealth.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELevels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20health%20tech%20company%20with%20an%20app%20that%20syncs%20with%20CGMs%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EControlling%20blood%20sugar%20may%20also%20help%20people%20address%20chronic%20health%20issues%20to%20manage%20or%20prevent%20long-term%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGayle%20Pagano%2C%20a%2056-year-old%20Florida%20resident%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20started%20using%20a%20CGM%20through%20Nutrisense%20after%20struggling%20with%20weight%20gain%20and%20joint%20pain.%20She%20was%20edging%20towards%20prediabetes%2C%20and%20doctors%20wrote%20it%20off%20as%20a%20natural%20side%20effect%20of%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20wearing%20a%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor%20and%20smiling%20while%20working%20out%20with%20resistance%20bands%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf86015da406397bf69f51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGayle%20Pagano%20said%20she%20lost%20weight%20and%20reduced%20her%20risk%20of%20diabetes%20by%20using%20a%20CGM.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gayle%20Pagano%2FNutrisense%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20basically%20had%20to%20get%20sick%20to%20have%20coverage%20for%20getting%20sick%2C%26quot%3B%20Pagano%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20reading%20about%20how%20age-related%20hormone%20changes%20can%20affect%20blood%20sugar%2C%20she%20started%20tracking%20hers%2C%20and%20noticed%20a%20pattern.%20Eating%20refined%20carbs%20like%20bread%20spiked%20her%20blood%20sugar%2C%20and%20she%20felt%20worse.%20Even%20ostensibly%20healthy%20foods%20like%20salads%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20if%20they%20were%20store-bought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20shocking.%20The%20things%20you%20would%20think%20are%20OK%20to%20eat%2C%20they're%20just%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20a%20nutritionist%2C%20she%20started%20making%20changes.%20Growing%20up%20in%20an%20Italian%20home%2C%20Pagano%20was%20reluctant%20to%20give%20up%20pasta%2C%20but%20found%20she%20could%20still%20enjoy%20some%20carbs%20with%20simple%20habits%20like%20making%20the%20noodles%20herself%20and%20eating%20protein%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20she's%20lost%2050%20pounds%2C%20and%20saw%20dramatic%20improvements%20to%20her%20fasting%20glucose%2C%20fasting%20insulin%2C%20and%20A1c%20(a%20measure%20of%20average%20blood%20sugar%20levels).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223def34a3-209e-4d69-b68c-604fa900d6af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20really%20prevent%20diseases%20by%20monitoring%20your%20blood%20sugar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPagano%20isn't%20alone%20in%20struggling%20to%20get%20medical%20care%20in%20the%20gray%20area%20between%20borderline%20health%20metrics%20and%20an%20active%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20typical%20healthcare%20paradigm%2C%20you%20may%20have%20to%20wait%20months%20or%20even%20years%20for%20regular%20checkups%20to%20detect%20a%20problem.%20Companies%20are%20positioning%20CGMs%20as%20a%20way%20to%20cut%20out%20the%20waiting%20game%20%E2%80%94%20what%20if%20you%20could%20proactively%20control%20your%20health%20before%20developing%20an%20illness%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20giving%20people%20access%20to%20their%20own%20health%20data%2C%20they%20can%20understand%20with%20a%20lot%20more%20clarity%20exactly%20where%20they%20stand%20and%20whether%20the%20choices%20they're%20making%20are%20having%20the%20impact%20that%20they%20want%20rather%20than%20having%20to%20wait%20six%20months%20or%20a%20year%20down%20the%20road%20for%20just%20a%20scrap%20of%20information%20given%20them%20to%20them%20by%20their%20doctor%2C%26quot%3B%20Means%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20it%20it%20isn't%20a%20matter%20of%20telling%20people%20to%20ditch%20carbs%20or%20start%20intermittent%20fasting.%20It's%20about%20giving%20people%20tools%20to%20understand%20what%20works%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECGMs%20are%20great%20giving%20you%20a%20peek%20at%20your%20body's%20inner%20workings%20in%20real%20time%2C%20accurately%20reflecting%20your%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20at%20a%20given%20moment%2C%20and%20showing%20how%20those%20levels%20change%20in%20response%20to%20certain%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20that%20science%20isn't%20very%20good%20at%20telling%20us%20exactly%20what%20those%20numbers%20mean%20yet.%20While%20CGMs%20can%20help%20people%20with%20diabetes%20avoid%20dangerous%20extremes%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%20what%20happens%20between%20those%20upper%20and%20lower%20extremes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20Pagano%20or%20Jacobs%20are%20wrong%20about%20the%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20means%20we're%20operating%20in%20a%20scientific%20gray%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cycling%20athlete%20in%20a%20helmet%20and%20sponsored%20jersey%20and%20shorts%20riding%20a%20bike%20with%20mountainous%20terrain%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf85351aa2ac29ee31ed4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEndurance%20athletes%20can%20use%20carbs%20to%20fuel%20long%20sessions%20of%20training%20or%20tough%20races%2C%20but%20cyclist%20Tracey%20Jacobs%20said%20she%20was%20overdoing%20it%20on%20sugar.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Dane%20Cronin%2FCourtesy%20of%20Tracey%20Jacobs%2C%20Groove%20Subaru%2FExcel%20Sports%20Race%20Team%20athlete%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20evidence.%20But%20just%20because%20there's%20no%20evidence%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20not%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20David%20Klonoff%2C%20an%20endocrinologist%20and%20medical%20director%20of%20a%20diabetes%20research%20institute%20in%20San%20Mateo%2C%20CA%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Klonoff%2C%20there's%20a%20risk%20that%20people%20investing%20in%20a%20CGM%20may%20get%20little%20in%20return%2C%20or%20could%20simple%20experience%20a%20kind%20of%20placebo%20effect%2C%20since%20paying%20more%20attention%20to%20your%20habits%20drives%20healthier%20behaviors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e40ac90-2a76-4d93-a753-ba54e89a6dba%5C%22%3EClean%20eating%20can%20be%20unhealthy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20are%20concerned%20that%20letting%20blood%20sugar%20dictate%20our%20diet%20too%20much%20could%20prompt%20extreme%20and%20unhealthy%20eating%20behaviors.%20Constant%20food%20monitoring%20can%20contribute%20to%20orthorexia%2C%20a%20detrimental%20fixation%20on%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bclean%26quot%3B%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221435%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20table%20with%20bowls%20of%20fruit%20including%20watermelon%2C%20pineapple%2C%20and%20berries%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf86f91aa2ac29ee31ee3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22957%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFruit%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20scary.%20Some%20social%20media%20influencers%20claim%20it's%20unhealthy%20because%20it%20can%20spike%20blood%20sugar%2C%20but%20that's%20an%20oversimplification%20and%20not%20the%20case%20for%20most%20people%2C%20according%20to%20experts%3Cp%3EJohner%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20influencers%20with%20no%20apparent%20medical%20expertise%20point%20to%20blood%20sugar%20spikes%20to%20warn%20against%20eating%20healthy%20foods%20like%20fruit%20or%20rice%2C%20saying%20they%20cause%20brain%20fog%2C%20weight%20gain%2C%20and%20various%20catastrophic%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisordered%20eating%20or%20having%20a%20poorer%20relationship%20with%20food%20is%20a%20significant%20issue%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20plausible%20that%20using%20a%20CGM%20or%20tracking%20could%20potentially%20lead%20certain%20people%20who%20are%20susceptible%20toward%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Jonathan%20Little%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20British%20Columbia%20who%20specializes%20in%20metabolism%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20doesn't%20support%20the%20fear%20that%20rising%20blood%20sugar%20after%20a%20meal%20is%20cause%20for%20concern%20in%20otherwise%20healthy%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20makes%20me%20perturbed%20is%20when%20people%20use%20statements%20like%20'those%20are%20prediabetes%20glucose%20levels'%2C%20or%20'I%20ate%20this%20and%20my%20glucose%20went%20to%20diabetes%20levels%2C'%26quot%3B%20Klonoff%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20the%20evidence%20to%20know%20that's%20a%20bad%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c916fb09-1e03-4726-9943-212217668e90%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20should%20you%20wear%20a%20CGM%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20predicts%20that%20CGMs%20will%20soon%20be%20another%20standard%20metric%20collected%20by%20everyday%20electronics%20along%20with%20data%20like%20our%20step%20count%2C%20heart%20rate%2C%20or%20sleep%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20want%20more%20information%20about%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20their%20bodies%2C%20and%20health%20wearables%20can%20also%20be%20a%20status%20symbol%20to%20tout%20your%20health-conscious%20cred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20is%20happy%20about%20this%20looming%20trend.%20People%20with%20diabetes%20have%20raised%20concerns%20that%20people%20who%20need%20the%20devices%20can't%20afford%20them%2C%20and%20rising%20popularity%20of%20the%20tech%20could%20make%20access%20even%20harder.%20However%2C%20widespread%20use%20could%20also%20drive%20innovations%2C%20like%20over-the-counter%20options%2C%20that%20may%20make%20CGMs%20cheaper%20for%20everyone%2C%20as%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ey.com%2Fen_ch%2Flife-sciences%2Fwhat-can-we-learn-from-the-continuous-glucose-monitoring-device-market%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAbbott%2520reportedly%2520ramped%2520down%2520pricing%2Cmuch%2520as%252066%2525%2520in%25202021.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarket%20reporting%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20and%20other%20metabolism%20experts%20are%20not%20convinced%20that%20wearables%20can%20give%20us%20more%20actionable%20data%20than%20we%20already%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20need%20an%20arm%20patch%20to%20make%20the%20point%20that%20nutrient-dense%20carbs%20like%20whole%20grains%20and%20fruit%20are%20healthy%2C%20or%20that%20chowing%20down%20on%20ultra-processed%20food%20may%20make%20you%20feel%20worse%20over%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20for%20the%20typical%20exercising%20person%20or%20person%20trying%20to%20optimize%20health%2C%20knowing%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20at%20every%20time%20of%20day%20is%20super%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20Little%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglucose-monitors-over-the-counter-track-blood-sugar-health-fitness-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724492042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf83461aa2ac29ee31ebe7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglucose-monitors-over-the-counter-track-blood-sugar-health-fitness-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20popular%20trend%