20craft%20stems%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fucrmagazinearchive.ucr.edu%2Fspring-2021-presto-chango%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatching%20legends%20like%20David%20Copperfield%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20David%20Blaine%2C%20and%20by%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20fooled%20badly%26quot%3B%20himself%2C%20he%20said.%20Chan%20picked%20up%20tricks%20through%20lectures%20at%20a%20magic%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast-forward%20a%20few%20decades%20to%20March%202020%2C%20when%20stay-at-home%20orders%20threatened%20to%20sideline%20Chan's%20business.%20But%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%20show-stopper%20for%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bmentalist%2C%26quot%3B%20whose%20shows%20are%20centered%20on%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20mind-reading%2C%20turned%20into%20a%20big%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20Chan%20got%20familiar%20with%20Zoom%20and%20discovered%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-favorite-magician-pivoting-to-zoom-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20video-calling%20service%20could%20take%20his%20business%20to%20new%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Soon%2C%20he%20was%20doing%20as%20many%20as%2012%20half-hour-long%20shows%20per%20day%2C%20earning%20up%20to%20%244%2C000%20per%20show%20by%20performing%20for%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-life-magician-hired-by-billionaires-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20billionaires%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirtual%20shows%20saved%20Chan%20from%20countless%20hours%20of%20traveling%2C%20even%20though%20it%20kept%20him%20from%20trading%20stories%20in%20person%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-performed-magic-elon-musk-paypal-20th-ipo-anniversary-party-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrities%20like%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20George%20Lucas%2C%20Paula%20Abdul%2C%20and%20Draymond%20Green%2C%20who%20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20icons%20he's%20met%20throughout%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20doing%20virtual%20shows%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20had%20so%20much%20free%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20stay%20busy%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Chan%20started%20reading%20more%20about%20investing%20and%2C%20like%20millions%20of%20others%2C%20made%20a%20habit%20of%20picking%20stocks%20himself.%20Family%20members%20tried%20to%20talk%20him%20out%20of%20it%20as%20the%20market%20seesawed.%20He's%20glad%20he%20didn't%20listen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b701b36-3597-4556-8b18-4287b2708fee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20invest%20like%20a%20magician%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20company%20he's%20nearly%20all-in%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20smoke%20and%20mirrors%20behind%20Chan's%20returns.%20The%20magician%20taught%20himself%20how%20to%20pick%20stocks%20and%20believes%20others%20can%20also%20create%20wealth%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20portfolio%20manager%20wants%20to%20charge%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20give%20them%20the%20money%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20doesn't%20require%20a%20finance%20background%20or%20a%20crystal%20ball.%20Even%20after%20managing%20money%20for%20years%20and%20beating%20the%20market%2C%20Chan%20doesn't%20pretend%20to%20be%20an%20expert.%20Those%20following%20in%20his%20footsteps%20shouldn't%20be%20afraid%20to%20take%20risks%2C%20especially%20on%20companies%20they%20know%20and%20believe%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvesting%20on%20your%20gut%20in%20the%20beginning%20and%20making%20small%20mistakes%20is%20crucial%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20wait%20to%20start%20investing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20strike%20out%2C%20but%20you're%20going%20to%20still%20need%20to%20swing%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said.%20%26quot%3BSwing%20for%20the%20fences%2C%20because%20I%20used%20to%20just%20shoot%20for%20first%20base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20fund%20managers%2C%20Chan%20glances%20at%20valuation%20metrics%20like%20price-to-earnings%20(P%2FE)%20ratios%20and%20looks%20at%20a%20company's%20debt%20load.%20But%20most%20of%20his%20investing%20strategy%20is%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20anecdotes%20and%20real-world%20experience.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20he%20sees%20out-the-door%20lines%20at%20Costco%20or%20has%20a%20bad%20experience%20with%20Tesla's%20customer%20service%2C%20he%20may%20buy%20or%20sell%20their%20respective%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20fascinating%20twist%20is%20that%20Chan%20buys%20at%20least%20one%20share%20of%20every%20company%20that%20hires%20him%20for%20a%20magic%20show%2C%20sometimes%20just%20to%20see%20how%20it%20performs.%20And%20when%20he%20has%20in-person%20shows%2C%20he%20looks%20for%20clues%20that%20give%20him%20insight%20into%20what's%20happening%20at%20the%20company%20behind%20closed%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20only%20one%20instance%20where%20I%20felt%20like%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20be%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said%2C%20naming%20the%20company%20off-the-record.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20the%20corporate%20culture%20was%20broken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20Chan%20became%20a%20believer%20in%20Nvidia%20after%20seeing%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20up%20close.%20He%20now%20has%20a%20hunch%20about%20how%20the%20chipmaker's%20valuation%20has%20defied%20gravity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJensen%20did%20a%20meet-and-greet%20with%20interns%2C%20and%20all%20the%20interns%20were%20lined%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20thinking%2C%20'Boy%2C%20if%20they%20did%20this%20recruiting%2C%20and%20people%20started%20finding%20out%20about%20this%2C%20people%20are%20going%20to%20want%20to%20work%20for%20Nvidia%20more.'%20Because%20Facebook%20doesn't%20do%20that%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20never%20heard%20of%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20showing%20up%20to%20an%20intern%20event.%20But%20the%20interns%20are%20the%20future%20of%20your%20company%2C%20and%20if%20you%20get%20them%20excited%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20work%20harder%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPull%20back%20the%20curtain%20on%20Chan's%20investments%2C%20and%20one%20company%20dwarfs%20the%20others%3A%20Alphabet.%20Over%2070%25%20of%20Chan's%20portfolio%20is%20in%20the%20Google-parent's%20Class%20A%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgoogl-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOOGL%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20Class%20C%20shares%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgoog-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOOG%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20his%20profit%20across%20those%20two%20positions%20is%20almost%20%24160%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20realized%20about%20Google%20was%2C%20whether%20you%20click%20on%20an%20ad%20or%20a%20kid%20clicks%20on%20an%20ad%20or%20you%20just%20watch%20something%20on%20YouTube%2C%20they%20make%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Chan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'That's%20a%20really%20good%20business%20model.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chan's%20favorite%20growth%20stocks%20go%20on%20sale%2C%20the%20magician%20usually%20buys%20the%20dip%2C%20though%20doing%20so%20for%20Alphabet%20has%20backfired%20lately%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he's%20starting%20to%20diversify%20away%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn't%20take%20a%20mind%20reader%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20professional%20money%20managers%20would%20say%20about%20Chan's%20strategy.%20They'd%20certainly%20scoff%20at%20his%20all-in%20approach%20and%20casual%20use%20of%20valuation%20metrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20fund%20managers%20trail%20the%20market%2C%20and%20Chan%20has%20beaten%20it%20soundly.%20Maybe%20the%20magician%20could%20teach%20those%20professional%20investors%20a%20trick%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-magician-dan-chan-millionaire-mentalist-strategy-stock-recommendation-ideas-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724491622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8da2dc72ebc54a40e71f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-magician-dan-chan-millionaire-mentalist-strategy-stock-recommendation-ideas-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Magician%20Dan%20Chan's%20most%20impressive%20act%20may%20be%20outperforming%20the%20stock%20market%20in%20the%20long%20term%20%E2%80%94%20without%20any%20tricks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40insider.com%20(James%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-magician-dan-chan-millionaire-mentalist-strategy-stock-recommendation-ideas-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Foreign%20Media%20Covered%20PM%20Modi's%20Visit%20To%20Ukraine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BMr%20Modi%20has%20carefully%20calibrated%20his%20country's%20relations%20with%20the%20two%20warring%20nations.%20On%20a%20trip%20to%20Moscow%20last%20month%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20hugged%20President%20Putin%2C%20and%20India%20has%20remained%20an%20important%20trading%20partner%20with%20Russia.%20India%20sent%20a%20representative%20to%20a%20Ukrainian-organised%20peace%20summit%20in%20June%20that%20Kyiv%20hoped%20would%20win%20backing%20for%20its%20negotiating%20positions%20in%20potential%20talks.%20But%20India%20did%20not%20join%20the%20nations%20that%20signed%20a%20communique%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summit%20supporting%20three%20points%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBBC%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BIndia%20had%20never%20been%20neutral%20in%20the%20war%2C%20he%20%5BPM%20Modi%5D%20insisted.%20'Right%20from%20the%20first%20day%20our%20side%20was%20peace%2C'%20Mr%20Modi%20argued%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20he%20came%20from%20the%20land%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20whose%20statue%20in%20Kyiv%20he%20visited%20earlier.%20But%20behind%20the%20language%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20India%20has%20never%20condemned%20Russia's%20full%20scale%20invasion%20and%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20has%20been%20helping%20to%20power%20Moscow's%20war%20economy%20with%20Delhi%20overtaking%20Beijing%20last%20month%20as%20the%20biggest%20importer%20of%20Russian%20oil%20-%20at%20a%20time%20it%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20Western%20sanctions.'%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Guardian%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20trip%20is%20the%20first%20to%20Ukraine%20by%20an%20Indian%20leader%20since%20the%20country's%201991%20independence%20from%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%20It%20follows%20a%20period%20of%20strained%20relations.%20Zelenskiy%20criticised%20Modi's%20recent%20trip%20to%20Moscow%2C%20which%20came%20on%20the%20same%20day%20Russian%20missiles%20flattened%20a%20children's%20hospital%20in%20Kyiv.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENikkei%20Asia%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BDespite%20Western%20pressure%2C%20India%20has%20not%20explicitly%20condemned%20traditional%20ally%20and%20weapons%20supplier%20Russia%20for%20invading%20Ukraine.%20Instead%2C%20it%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20resolving%20the%20conflict%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20South%20Asian%20country%20has%20been%20doing%20brisk%20business%20with%20Moscow%2C%20particularly%20through%20buying%20discounted%20Russian%20oil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELe%20Monde%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%26quot%3BZelensky%20called%20Modi's%20visit%20a%20'historic%20moment.'%20But%20neither%20side%20showed%20signs%20of%20a%20breakthrough%2C%20with%20Indian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Subrahmanyam%20Jaishankar%20later%20saying%20that%20it%20was%2