3EWhat%20has%20changed%20is%20the%20minority%20of%20Republicans%20in%20tech%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20motivated%20by%20concerns%20about%20regulating%20cryptocurrency%20or%20support%20for%20Israel%20%E2%80%94%20have%20become%20more%20emboldened%20to%20share%20their%20views%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20has%20caused%20Democrats%20to%20amp%20up%20their%20support%20for%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20an%20airing%20of%20grievances%20that%20we%20don't%20normally%20see%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Leslie%20Feinzaig%2C%20founder%20of%20VCs%20for%20Kamala.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20has%20been%20more%20emblematic%20of%20the%20shift%20than%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20endorsed%20Trump%20last%20month%20and%20hosted%20a%20rambling%20interview%20with%20him%20last%20week%20on%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20X.%20The%20former%20president%20has%20also%20received%20endorsements%20from%20famous%20VCs%20Marc%20Andreessen%2C%20Ben%20Horowitz%2C%20Doug%20Leone%2C%20and%20David%20Sacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hand-wringing%20Silicon%20Valley%20had%20gone%20red%2C%20liberal%20voices%20like%20LinkedIn%20cofounder%20Reid%20Hoffman%2C%20Netflix%20cofounder%20Reed%20Hastings%2C%20and%20venture%20investor%20Ron%20Conway%20affirmed%20their%20support%20for%20Harris.%20More%20than%20800%20investors%20have%20signed%20onto%20VCs%20for%20Kamala.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20Feinzaig%2C%20whose%20day%20job%20is%20managing%20the%20early-stage%20firm%20Graham%20%26amp%3B%20Walker%2C%20is%20not%20entirely%20comfortable%20being%20an%20advocate.%20She%20would%20much%20rather%20be%20spending%20her%20time%20making%20deals%20and%20helping%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20believe%20that%20I%2C%20of%20all%20people%2C%20became%20a%20political%20spokesperson%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Feinzaig.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20no%20politics%20rule%20at%20Graham%20and%20Walker.%20We%20try%20to%20just%20respect%20all%20views.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271fef7db-4314-4e