20has%20also%20been%20a%20factor%20in%20companies%20delaying%20their%20plans%20to%20go%20public%20until%20after%20November%2C%20according%20to%20Cameron%20Lester%2C%20global%20co-head%20of%20technology%2C%20media%2C%20and%20telecom%20investment%20banking%20at%20Jefferies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20really%20noisy%20time%20with%20the%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServiceTitan%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles-based%20startup%20that%20makes%20software%20to%20help%20tradespeople%20manage%20their%20businesses%2C%20was%20originally%20targeting%20this%20fall%20to%20go%20public.%20Now%2C%20executives%20are%20waiting%20until%20after%20the%20election%20concludes%20to%20make%20any%20decision%2C%20according%20to%20a%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20(ServiceTitan%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fc1abcf-8050-4c37-bfa2-0038aa70ebcc%5C%22%3ELimited%20partners%20are%20'irritated'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outspokenness%20of%20VCs%20is%20also%20causing%20consternation%20among%20the%20limited%20partners%20who%20fund%20venture%20firms%2C%20according%20to%20two%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20wanted%20our%20VCs%20to%20just%20shut%20their%20mouths%20and%20do%20their%20job%20and%20not%20be%20political%20unless%20they're%20defending%20the%20startup%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20LP%20who%20has%20backed%20many%20prominent%20VC%20funds%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20and%20New%20York.%20%26quot%3BOther%20than%20that%2C%20they%20shouldn't%20be%20posturing%20for%20a%20political%20candidate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublicly%20supporting%20candidates%20has%20no%20upside%20for%20LPs%2C%20especially%20considering%20many%20LPs%20have%20their%20own%20agendas%2C%20added%20a%20VC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20LPs%20are%20very%20irritated%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20VC.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20hired%20you%20to%20be%20a%20mechanic%2C%20I%20just%20wanted%20you%20to%20fix%20my%20car%20and%20not%20spend%20your%20time%20being%20a%20political%20advocate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20out%20a%20pension%20fund%20for%20union%20workers%20cannot%20be%20thrilled%20with%20a%20VC%20who%20endorses%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20spoken%20out%20against%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20most%20LPs%20worry%20about%20is%20the%20headline%20risk%20for%20you%20as%20a%20reporter%20to%20write%20an%20article%20and%20mention%20one%20of%20their%20general%20partners%2C%20and%20then%20they%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20their%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20LP.%20%26quot%3BIt%20stresses%20them%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20according%20to%20another%20VC%2C%20for%20all%20their%20dismay%2C%20most%20LPs%20are%20unlikely%20to%20do%20anything%20beyond%20voicing%20their%20displeasure%20in%20a%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20making%20money%20for%20LPs%2C%20they%20don't%20care%20what%20political%20persuasion%20you%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20VC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-a-distraction-silicon-valley-wants-to-be-over-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724490002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c792e51aa2ac29ee337b28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-a-distraction-silicon-valley-wants-to-be-over-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20outspokenness%20of%20VCs%20is%20causing%20consternation%20among%20LPs%20and%20the%20election%20is%20delaying%20IPOs%20and%20slowing%20dealmaking%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bbergman%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Bergman%2CMelia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-a-distraction-silicon-valley-wants-to-be-over-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20From%20Bhang%20Chutney%20To%20Olan%2C%20Indian%20Food%20Was%20Never%20Inherently%20Unhealthy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Feqprjhf8_indian-food_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20having%20a%20bout%20of%20the%20stomach%20flu%2C%20I%20sat%20last%20weekend%20in%20my%20bed%20waiting%20for%20my%20piping%20hot%C2%A0%3Ci%3Ekhichdi%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Efor%20lunch.%20As%20I%20took%20my%20first%20bite%2C%20I%20realised%20what%20an%20absolutely%20brilliant%20dish%20it%20is.%20Rice%20and%20legumes%20cooked%20together%20to%20make%20a%20healthy%2C%20satiating%20meal%20that%20your%20gut%20loves.%20There's%20a%20reason%20every%20Indian%20doctor%20prescribes%20it%20with%20your%20dose%20of%20antibiotics%20when%20your%20stomach%20is%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI've%20realised%20that%20Indian%20food%2C%20at%20its%20heart%2C%20and%20contrary%20to%20popular%20perception%2C%20is%20extremely%20healthy%20and%20delicious.%20It's%20not%20all%20oil%20and%20spices%2C%20as%20today's%20most%20popular%20Indian%20fare%20would%20like%20you%20to%20believe.%20So%20while%20I%20nursed%20my%20bad%20stomach%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20some%20research%20and%20call%20up%20a%20few%20friends%20from%20around%20India%20asking%20them%20about%20their%20favourite%20comfort%20foods%20that%20are%20also%20considered%20extremely%20healthy%20in%20their%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThalipeeth%20From%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20savoury%20multigrain%20flatbread%20made%20of%20sorghum%20(jowar)%2C%20wheat%2C%20pearl%20millet%20(bajra)%20and%20rice%2C%20along%20with%20roasted%20legumes%20(bengal%20gram%20and%20split%20black%20lentils).%20To%20this%20are%20added%20fresh%20onions%20and%20coriander%2C%20along%20with%20cumin%20seeds.%20A%20deliciously%20healthy%20low-fat%20bread%20that's%20also%20great%20for%20gut%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShakkariya%20No%20Shiro%20From%20Gujarat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sweet%20potato%20halwa%20made%20during%C2%A0%3Ci%3Enavratris%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eor%20any%20auspicious%20day%20of%20fasting%2C%20%E2%80%98shakkariya%20no%20shiro'%20is%20perhaps%20one%20of%20the%20healthiest%20halwas%20you'll%20find.%20Due%20to%20the%20natural%20sweetness%20of%20sweet%20potato%2C%20the%20added%20sugar%20is%20negligible%20when%20compared%20to%20any%20other%20halwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmita%20Khar%20From%20Assam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Khar'%20is%20an%20ancient%20ingredient%20from%20Assam%20mentioned%20in%20ancient%20texts%20like%C2%A0%3Ci%3EYogini%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0%3Ci%3ETantra%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eand%20is%20hailed%20for%20its%20antiseptic%20and%20antibacterial%20properties.%20It%20is%20made%20differently%20across%20Assam.%20While%20some%20use%20the%20ashes%20of%20papaya%20tree%20bark%20or%20stems%2C%20others%20use%20the%20ash%20of%20banana%20peels.%20Typically%20though%2C%20the%20dish%20requires%20banana%20peels%20that%20are%20sun-dried%20and%20then%20burnt%20to%20ashes.%20After%20that%2C%20water%20is%20filtered%20through%20these%20ashes%20overnight%2C%20and%20the%20astringent%2C%20alkaline%20dark%20brown%20liquid%20is%20then%20cooked%20with%20raw%20papaya%20and%20pulses%2C%20along%20with%20a%20protein%20of%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20if%20one%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhaang%20Ki%20Chutney%20From%20Uttarakhand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20hemp%20seeds%2C%20this%20chutney%20made%20with%20green%20chillies%2C%20coriander%20and%20a%20splash%20of%20lemon%20is%20a%20power%20punch%20of%20health.%20Hemp%20seeds%20are%20known%20for%20their%20nutritional%20value%20as%20they%20have%20over%20nine%20types%20of%20amino%20acids%20that%20aid%20in%20the%20release%20of%20happy%20hormones%20in%20the%20body.%20Eaten%20in%20every%20household%20and%20added%20to%20other%20dishes%2C%20this%20main%20staple%20of%20Uttarakhand%20is%20a%20delicious%20and%20healthy%20relish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOlan%20From%20Kerala%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMade%20of%20ash%20gourd%2C%20this%20mild%20sweet%20curry%20is%20simmered%20to%20perfection%20with%20cowpeas%2C%20coconut%20milk%2C%20ginger%20and%20curry%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENadir%20Yakhin%20From%20Kashmir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMade%20with%20lotus%20stems%20in%20a%20yoghourt-based%20curry%2C%20this%20quintessential%20Kashmiri%20dish%20is%20the%20star%20of%20vegetarian%20food.%20It%20is%20a%20sour%20curry%20that%20is%20good%20for%20the%20gut%20and%20light%20on%20the%20stomach%2C%20with%20just%20fennel%20powder%2C%20dried%20mint%20and%20cumin%20used%20for%20flavouring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESinghare%20Ki%20Kachri%20From%20Moradabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECraving%20a%20tangy%20street-style%20snack%20that%20does%20not%20have%20anything%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20fried%E2%80%9D%3F%20Singhare%20ki%20Kachri%20is%20made%20from%20pressure-cooked%20and%20mashed%20water%20chestnuts%20flavoured%20with%20cumin%20powder%2C%20black%20salt%2C%20red%20chilli%20powder%20and%20lemon.%20It%20is%20super%20tasty%20and%20packed%20with%20healthy%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhutte%20Ka%20Kees%20From%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20simple%20yet%20scrumptious%20dish%20of%20corn%20slowly%20simmered%20in%20skimmed%20milk%20along%20with%20spices%2C%20mustard%20seeds%20and%20green%20chillies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERugra%20From%20Jharkhand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERugra%20is%20an%20edible%20mushroom%20indigenous%20to%20Jharkhand.%20Rich%20in%20protein%20and%20essential%20micronutrients%2C%20Rugra%20is%20found%20growing%20under%20%E2%80%98Sal'%20trees%20during%20early%20monsoons.%20Cooked%20with%20minimal%20spices%2C%20this%20dish%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20among%20locals%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20growth%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3Erugra%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Ehas%20been%20impacted%20by%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShukhto%20From%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Sukhto%20needs%20no%20introduction%2C%20this%20palette%20cleanser%20is%20used%20by%20Bengalis%20to%20commence%20any%20feast.%20It's%20a%20stew%20made%20with%20an%20assortment%20of%20vegetables.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20renowned%20Bengali%20melody%20mentions%20this%20dish%2C%20whose%20lyrics%20go%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Rani%20lacks%20culinary%20expertise%3B%20she%20mistakenly%20adds%C2%A0%3Ci%3Echilli%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eto%20Shuktoni%2FShukto%E2%80%9D%2C%20suggesting%20how%20chillies%20are%20a%20big%20no-no%20in%20this%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChakhwi%20From%20Tripura%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakhwi%20is%20a%20traditional%20tribal%20dish%20made%20by%20slowly%20braising%20pork%20or%20chicken%20with%20bamboo%20shoots%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20drumstick%20leaf%2C%20fresh%20lemon%20leaves%20and%20green%20papaya.%20There's%20a%20burst%20of%20flavour%20in%20every%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOle%20Chutney%20From%20Bihar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20yams%20in%20Bihar%20households%2C%20this%20chutney%20is%20slowly%20disappearing%20from%20public%20memory.%20Why%3F%20Because%20yams%20are%20hard%20to%20handle%2C%20and%20often%20cause%20itching.%20Nevertheless%2C%20this%20mustard-flavoured%20chutney%20made%20just%20with%20mustard%20oil%2C%20mustard%20seeds%2C%20limes%2C%20green%20chillies%2C%20red%20chilli%20powder%20and%20turmeric%20powder%2C%20is%20packed%20with%20antioxidants%20and%20is%20good%20for%20the%20gut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20hidden%20gems%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20food.%20We%20just%20need%20to%20dig%20a%20little%20deeper%20into%20our%20heritage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5