div%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20credited%20the%20Nobel%20laureate%20Mr%20Yunus'%20track%20record%20and%20his%20acceptance%20in%20the%20international%20community%20as%20a%20strong%20point%20for%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20urge%20the%20credibility%20of%20our%20chief%20adviser%20is%20also%20a%20major%20factor.%20The%20acceptability%20both%20internationally%20among%20governments%20and%20institutions%20and%20our%20people%20who%20are%20now%20geared%20and%20so%20motivated%20in%20rebuilding%20the%20country%20and%20the%20economy%2C%20I%20think%20we%20are%20on%20the%20right%20track.%20Of%20course%2C%20no%20one%20said%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20easy.%20I%20think%20we%20are%20returning%20on%20strong%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murshid%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Attacks%20On%20Minorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murshid%2C%20while%20accepting%20there%20have%20been%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20denied%20large-scale%20targeting%20of%20minorities%20on%20religious%20grounds.%20Instead%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20violence%20reported%20from%20across%20Bangladesh%20was%20linked%20to%20political%20affiliation%20and%20not%20communal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhs%20of%20Hindus%20had%20taken%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20Bangladesh%20on%20August%2011%20to%20protest%20against%20attacks%20on%20the%20community%20after%20Ms%20Hasina%20resigned%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20fled%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20insecurity%20of%20vulnerable%20groups%20-%20call%20them%20minorities%20if%20you%20like%20-%20this%20government%20is%20making%20fundamental%2C%20philosophical%20changes.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20do%20not%20want%20to%20refer%20to%20anybody%20as%20minority.%20As%20professor%20Yunus%20said%2C%20we%20are%20one%20family.%20The%20violence%20that%20took%20place%20in%20specific%20categories%20have%20been%20because%20of%20the%20political%20turmoil.%20It%20was%20never%20because%20of%20communalism.%20This%20is%20where%20Indian%20media%20needs%20to%20come%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murshid%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20certain%20categories%20of%20communities%20that%20belong%20to%20certain%20political%20parties.%20The%20regime%20that%20has%20just%20been%20dethroned%2C%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20so-called%20minorities%2C%20actually%20had%20loyalty%20towards%20that%20political%20party.%20Mind%20you%2C%20in%20this%20change%20and%20shift%2C%20the%20violence%20that%20Awami%20League%20perpetrated%20on%20its%20own%20people%20have%20caused%20certain%20backlash%20against%20the%20Awami%20League%20as%20a%20party%20and%20its%20cadre%20who%20have%20systematically%20killed%20people.%20You%20must%20see%20it%20in%20that%20frame%20of%20reference%2C%20not%20in%20the%20frame%20of%20minorities%20as%20Hindus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20social%20welfare%20adviser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Folckobog_bangladeshprotest_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Are%20Not%20A%20Communal%20Nation%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20yesterday%2C%20our%20young%20people%2C%20people%20from%20the%20masjids%20have%20been%20protecting%20temples%20and%20communities.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20some%20lapses%20haven't%20happened.%20I%20won't%20say%20that.%20Some%20lapses%20have%20happened.%20But%20you%20must%20understand%20that%20we%20are%20not%20a%20communal%20nation.%20It%20is%20politics%20that%20use%20communalism%20to%20create%20communalism.%20We%20will%20rectify%20that%2C%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20that%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20request%20the%20Indian%20audience%2C%20please%20be%20sensitive%20about%20this.%20Remember%2C%20in%20this%20region%20of%20South%20Asia%2C%20we%20have%20had%20a%20long%20history%20of%20communal%20struggles.%20Anything%20that%20happens%20in%20India%20affects%20us.%20If%20there%20is%20violence%20on%20Christians%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Manipuris%20in%20your%20country%2C%20then%20that%20has%20direct%20impact%20on%20security%20in%20my%20country.%20I%20think%20when%20you%20ask%20me%20about%20future%20policies%2C%20I%20think%20they%20must%20be%20much%20more%20compassionate%2C%20much%20more%20understanding%2C%20much%20more%20sensitive.%20We%20need%20to%20work%20towards%20that%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murshid%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%2C%2076%2C%20resigned%20as%20Bangladesh's%20Prime%20Minister%20earlier%20this%20month%20following%20weeks%20of%20deadly%20protests%20that%20began%20as%20demonstrations%20by%20students%20against%20government%20job%20quotas%2C%20but%20surged%20into%20a%20movement%20demanding%20her%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20retained%20power%20for%20a%20fourth%20straight%20term%20in%20an%20election%20in%20January%20boycotted%20by%20the%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%2C%20which%20had%20accused%20her%20Awami%20League%20of%20trying%20to%20legitimise%20sham%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh's%20flagging%20economy%2C%20once%20among%20the%20world's%20fastest%20growing%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20country's%20booming%20garments%20sector%2C%20has%20stagnated.%20Inflation%20hovers%20around%2010%20per%20cent%20and%20dollar%20reserves%20are%20shrinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ms%20Hasina%20left%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Anti-Discrimination%20Student%20Movement%20proposed%20the%20name%20of%20Mr%20Yunus%20to%20head%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724488680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcli9gksg_sharmeen-murshid_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht