%20remains%20established%20with%20the%20FTL%20area%20to%20prevent%20encroachments%20upon%20water%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20zonal%20commissioners%20of%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC)%20were%20tasked%20with%20forming%20lake%20protection%20committees%20to%20prevent%20encroachments%20upon%20water%20bodies%20in%20and%20around%20the%20city.%20Recently%2C%20the%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%20(NRSC)%20has%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20extent%20of%20lakes%20in%20Hyderabad%20was%20reduced%20by%2061%20per%20cent%20between%201979%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagarjuna's%20Convention%20Centre%20allegedly%20stood%20on%201.12%20acre%20of%20the%20FTL%20area%20and%20an%20additional%202%20acre%20within%20the%20buffer%20zone.%20According%20to%20official%20sources%2C%20the%20FTL%20area%20of%20Thammidikunta%20Lake%20is%20approximately%2029.24%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20was%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20several%20years.%20However%2C%20the%20GHMC%20had%20not%20taken%20any%20action%20against%20it.%20The%20management%20of%20the%20convention%20centre%20allegedly%20used%20influence%20to%20bypass%20regulatory%20actions%20from%20concerned%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20complaint%20against%20the%20convention%20centre%20was%20filed%20to%20HYDRA%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%2C%20Telangana's%20Minister%20of%20Roads%20and%20Buildings.%20He%20also%20enclosed%20with%20his%20complaint%20the%20FTL%20map%20pointing%20out%20the%20encroachment%20along%20with%20a%20Google%20Earth%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20took%20to%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20following%20the%20demolition%20drive.%20%26quot%3BThe%20land%20is%20a%20Patta%20land%2C%20and%20not%20even%20an%20inch%20of%20tank%20plan%20is%20encroached.%20As%20a%20law-abiding%20citizen%2C%20if%20the%20Court%20before%20which%20the%20matter%20is%20pending%2C%20had%20decided%20against%20me%2C%20I%20would%20have%20carried%20out%20the%20demolition%20myself.%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPained%20by%20the%20unlawful%20manner%20of%20demolition%20carried%20out%20in%20respect%20of%20N%20Convention%2C%20contrary%20to%20existing%20stay%20orders%20and%20Court%20cases.%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20thought%20it%20fit%20to%20issue%20this%20statement%20to%20place%20on%20record%20certain%20facts%20for%20protecting%20my%20reputation%20and%20to%20indicate%20that%20we%20have%20not%20done%20any%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nagarjuna%20Akkineni%20(%40iamnagarjuna)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiamnagarjuna%2Fstatus%2F1827242881674850568%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20no%20notice%20was%20issued%20to%20him%20prior%20to%20the%20demolition%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%20recently%20constituted%20HYDRA%20for%20Telangana%20Core%20Urban%20Region%20(TCUR)%20for%20disaster%20management%2C%20asset%20protection%20and%20other%20functions.%20They%20are%20responsible%20for%20managing%20and%20protecting%20government%20assets%20such%20as%20parks%2C%20layout%20open%20spaces%2C%20playgrounds%2C%20and%20lakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHYDRA%20is%20headed%20by%20IPS%20officer%20AV%20Ranganath%20and%20it%20has%20been%20demolishing%20illegal%20structures%20in%20the%20state%20to%20reclaim%20encroached%20land%20of%20water%20bodies.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20they%20demolished%20unauthorised%20constructions%20in%20the%20heritage%20lake%20Bum-Rukn-Ud-Dowla%20in%20Shastripuram%2C%20and%20near%20the%20Gandipet%20reservoir%20in%20Rangareddy%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724487180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F1ll82hcg_nagarjuna-_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%