20detonation%20of%20explosive%20materials.%20Authorities%20imposed%20emergency%20measures%20and%20evacuated%20200%20people%20in%20the%20Ostrogozhsky%20district.%20No%20casualties%20were%20reported%2C%20but%20risks%20remain%20as%20drone%20warfare%20continues%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-again-declares-emergency-in-voronezh-after-ukrainian-drone-attacks%2Farticleshow%2F112758464.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-again-declares-emergency-in-voronezh-after-ukrainian-drone-attacks%2Famp_articleshow%2F112758464.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-again-declares-emergency-in-voronezh-after-ukrainian-drone-attacks%2Famp_articleshow%2F112758464.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Takes%20Over%20Kolkata%20Horror%20Case%2C%20Lie%20Detector%20Tests%20Of%20Accused%20Begin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20main%20accused%2C%20Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20will%20undergo%20the%20polygraph%20test%20at%20the%20prison%20where%20he%20is%20currently%20lodged.%20The%20remaining%20six%20individuals%20-%20%C2%A0former%20principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20four%20doctors%20who%20were%20on%20duty%20during%20the%20night%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20a%20civil%20volunteer%20-%20will%20have%20their%20tests%20administered%20at%20the%20CBI%20office.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20specialised%20team%20from%20the%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(CFSL)%20in%20Delhi%20has%20been%20dispatched%20to%20Kolkata%20to%20carry%20out%20these%20polygraph%20tests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20CBI%20informed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20there%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20tamper%20with%20evidence%20at%20the%20crime%20scene%20before%20the%20central%20agency%20took%20over%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%208-9.%20According%20to%20CBI%20sources%2C%20the%20victim%20had%20dinner%20with%20two%20first-year%20postgraduate%20trainees%20around%20midnight.%20After%20their%20meal%2C%20the%20trio%20retreated%20to%20the%20seminar%20room%2C%20where%20they%20watched%20athlete%20Neeraj%20Chopra's%20javelin%20event%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAt%202%3A00%20am%2C%20the%20two%20trainees%20left%20the%20seminar.%20The%20victim%2C%20however%2C%20chose%20to%20stay%20behind.%20An%20intern%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20on%20the%20third%20floor%20that%20night%2C%20claimed%20to%20have%20remained%20in%20the%20interns'%20room%2C%20which%20was%20situated%20nearby.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20around%209%3A30%20am%2C%20one%20of%20the%20postgraduate%20trainees%20who%20had%20dined%20with%20the%20victim%20went%20to%20check%20on%20her%20before%20the%20start%20of%20ward%20rounds.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20he%20discovered%20her%20body.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Kolkata%20Police%20said%20that%20the%20trainee%20found%20the%20victim%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20motionless%20state%20from%20a%20distance%26quot%3B%20and%20alerted%20his%20colleagues%20and%20senior%20doctors%2C%20who%20then%20informed%20the%20hospital%20authorities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20CBI's%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20crucial%20evidence%20linking%20some%20of%20the%20individuals%20being%20probed.%20Fingerprints%20of%20two%20of%20the%20four%20doctors%20were%20found%20in%20the%20seminar%20room%20where%20the%20victim's%20body%20was%20discovered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20hospital%20also%20provides%20a%20timeline%20of%20the%20movements%20of%20key%20individuals%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%20crime.%20Sanjay%20Roy%20was%20captured%20on%20camera%20entering%20the%20college%20at%201%3A03%20am%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%20crime.%20The%20footage%20shows%20him%20with%20a%20Bluetooth%20earphone%20coiled%20around%20his%20neck%20-%20a%20crucial%20detail%2C%20as%20a%20similar%20Bluetooth%20device%20was%20found%20at%20the%20crime%20scene%20during%20the%20initial%20investigation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20case%20has%20ignited%20widespread%20protests%20across%20India%2C%20with%20particularly%20intense%20demonstrations%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ordered%20the%20deployment%20of%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%20personnel%20to%20the%20hospital%20to%20bolster%20security%20measures%20around%20the%20institution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724485560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvpd4a1mo_kolkata-rape-_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-case-rg-kar-cbi-takes-over-kolkata-horror-case-polygraph-tests-of-accused-begin-6407145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20today%20began%20conducting%20lie%20detection%20tests%20on%20the%20primary%20accused%20and%20six%20others%20connected%20to%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20the%20state-run%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-case-rg-kar-cbi-takes-over-kolkata-horror-case-polygraph-tests-of-accused-begin-6407145%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sarabjot%20Makes%20Big%20Olympics%20Revelation%2C%20Says%20He%20Barely%20Trained%20With%20Bhaker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESarabjot%20Singh%2C%20who%20partnered%20with%20Manu%20Bhaker%20to%20win%20India's%20first%20ever%20Olympic%20medal%20in%20a%20mixed%20shooting%20event%2C%20on%20Saturday%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bbarely%26quot%3B%20got%20to%20train%20together%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20their%20event.%20Bhaker%20and%20Sarabjot%20scripted%20history%20with%20a%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20shooting%20event%20at%20the%20Paris%20Games.%20%26quot%3BMy%20training%20was%20due%20at%209%2C%20hers%20was%20due%20at%2012%2C%20individually.%20Mixed%20session%20lasted%20for%2030%20minutes%2C%20before%20which%20she%20trained%20separately%2C%20and%20I%20separately.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOur%20conversation%20was%20usually%20brief%20and%20limited%20to%20'Apna%20100%20per%20cent%20dena%20hai%20(we%20have%20to%20give%20our%20100%20per%20cent)'.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20some%20banter.%20Sometimes%20I%20would%20make%20fun%20of%20her%2C%20sometimes%20she%20would%20of%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Sarabjot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarabjot%20also%20revealed%20his%20longtime%20fandom%20for%20Yusuf%20Dikec%20and%20said%20he%20has%20been%20looking%20up%20to%20the%20Turkish%20shooting%20icon%20for%20inspiration%20since%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20watching%20his%20(Yusuf's)%20videos%20since%202011.%20He%20has%20always%20been%20like%20this.%20He%20is%2051%20today.%20Even%20though%20I%20have%20tried%2C%20I%20could%20not%20match%20his%20perfection.%20If%20I%20had%20the%20chance%2C%20I%20would%20ask%20him%20what%20he%20eats%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2022-year-old%20from%20Dheen%20village%20of%20Haryana%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20PUMA%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarabjot%20said%20that%20his%20pistol%20is%20engraved%20with%20SSINGH30%2C%20comprising%20his%20initials%20and%20a%20significant%20date%20in%20his%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20give%20it%20a%20name.%20When%20I%20achieved%20my%20personal%20best%20at%20the%202022%20Asian%20Games%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20I%20got%20the%20weapon%20engraved%20with%20'SSINGH30'.%20That%20is%20my%20best%20weapon.%20Because%20my%20medal%20(gold)%20came%20on%20September%2030%20and%20that%20was%20a%20significant%20achievement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20athlete%20also%20shared%20that%20he%20has%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20his%20fair%20share%20of%20setbacks%20in%20his%20journey.%20Meditation%2C%20and%20a%20rare%20yogic%20technique%20called%20Trataka%2C%20helped%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20technique%20is%20to%20look%20at%20the%20candle%20flame%20with%20eyes%20open%20for%20three%20minutes%2C%20and%20then%20imagine%20for%20two%20minutes.%20I%20used%20to%20keep%20it%20directly%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComplete%20darkness%20in%20the%20room%2C%20complete%20peace%2C%20silence.%20My%20eyes%20would%20water%3B%20it%20was%20not%20easy.%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20visualisation%20in%20shooting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sarabjot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20the%20Olympic%20medallist%20stated%20his%20ambition%20for%20the%202028%20Los%20Angeles%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLA%20'28%3B%20iska%20colour%20change%20karna%20hai%20(LA%20'28%2C%20I%20want%20to%20change%20its%20colour)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sarabjot%2C%20gesturing%20toward%20his%20glittering%20bronze%20medal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724485260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9l600bg8_sarabjot-singh_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fsarabjot-singh-makes-big-paris-olympics-2024-revelation-says-he-barely-trained-with-manu-bhaker-6407085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarabjot%20Singh%2C%20who%20partnered%20with%20Manu%20Bhaker%20to%20win%20India's%20first%20ever%20Olympic%20medal%20in%20a%20mixed%20shooting%20event%2C%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bbarely%26quot%3B%20got%20to%20train%20together%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20their%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fsarabjot-singh-makes-big-paris-olympics-2024-revelation-says-he-barely-