er%20hair%20was%20cut%20in%20captivity.%20She%20also%20added%20that%20she%20was%20injured%20in%20a%20wall%20collapse%20incident%20caused%20by%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Ms%20Argamani%20narrated%20her%20ordeal%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20diplomats%20from%20Israel%20and%20G7%20countries%20in%20Tokyo.%20However%2C%20she%20later%20clarified%20that%20her%20words%20were%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20ignore%20what%20the%20Israeli%20media%20has%20done%20to%20me%20over%20the%20past%2024%20hours%2C%20taking%20my%20words%20out%20of%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20Instagram%20stories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAl%20Qassam%20Brigades'%20members%20did%20not%20hit%20me%20while%20I%20was%20in%20captivity%2C%20nor%20did%20they%20cut%20my%20hair%3B%20I%20was%20injured%20by%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20wall%20caused%20by%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Argamani%20underlined%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20hit%20me%20during%20captivity%2C%20but%20I%20was%20injured%20all%20over%20my%20body%20after%20the%20airstrike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fpf9t606_noa-agramani-_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20image%20caption%20here%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2026-year-old%20was%20among%20the%20hundreds%20of%20people%20kidnapped%20by%20Hamas%20from%20the%20Nova%20music%20festival%20during%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20freed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20special%20forces%20in%20a%20raid%20on%20the%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Gaza%20on%20June%208.%20Besides%20her%2C%20three%20others%20--%20Almog%20Meir%20Jan%2C%2022%2C%20Andrey%20Kozlov%2C%2027%2C%20and%20Shlomi%20Ziv%2C%2041%20--%20were%20freed%2C%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20visit%20to%20Japan%20with%20her%20father%2C%20Ms%20Argamani%20recalled%20the%20time%20she%20was%20held%20captive%20by%20the%20Hamas%20militants.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20night%20I%20was%20falling%20asleep%20and%20thinking%2C%20this%20may%20be%20the%20last%20night%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTill%20the%20time%20she%20was%20rescued%20by%20the%20Israeli%20authorities%2C%20Ms%20Argamani%20%26quot%3Bjust%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20I'm%20still%20surviving%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20miracle%20because%20I%20survived%20October%207%2C%20and%20I%20survived%20this%20bombing%2C%20and%20I%20also%20survived%20the%20rescue%2C%26quot%3B%20AFP%20quoted%20her%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20video%20showing%20Ms%20Argamani%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20motorcycle%20screaming%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20kill%20me%26quot%3B%2C%20went%20viral.%20The%20video%20also%20showed%20her%20boyfriend%20--%20Avinatan%20Or%2C%20an%20engineer%20--%20being%20taken%20away%20separately.%20However%2C%20she%20has%20clarified%20that%20she%20had%20no%20idea%20about%20it%20until%20she%20was%20freed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAvinatan%2C%20my%20boyfriend%2C%20is%20still%20there%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20bring%20them%20back%20before%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20had%20retrieved%20the%20bodies%20of%20six%20hostages%20from%20various%20tunnels%20in%20the%20southern%20region%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20251%20people%20were%20taken%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%20last%20year.%20Of%20these%2C%20105%2C%20including%2034%20dead%2C%20are%20still%20inside%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Israeli%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%201%2C200%20people%20in%20Israel%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20October%207%20attack.%20Over%20