20exactly%20two%20years%20ago.%20The%20very%20next%20day%2C%20on%20February%2025%2C%202022%2C%20India%20abstained%20from%20voting%20on%20a%20draft%20resolution%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council.%20In%20the%20course%20of%20the%20ongoing%20war%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20abstaining%20from%20taking%20clear%20sides%2C%20much%20to%20the%20chagrin%20of%20establishments%20in%20both%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20the%20United%20States.%20As%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visits%20Ukraine%2C%20after%20a%20much-publicised%20visit%20to%20Moscow%20in%20July%2C%20in%20maintaining%20with%20India's%20stated%20position%20of%20strategic%20neutrality%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20asked%20in%20global%20capitals%20about%20India's%20motivations.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20an%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20has%20visited%20an%20independent%20Ukraine%20after%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20enough%20domestic%20discussions%20on%20India's%20purported%20role%20in%20world%20peace%20and%20other%20grand%20enterprise.%20Let's%20bring%20realism%20back%20into%20the%20game%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecoupling%20From%20West%20Is%20Not%20An%20Option%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDomestic%20chatter%20aside%2C%20what%20the%20Western%20world%20-%20the%20US%2C%20EU%2C%20UK%20nexus%20-%20thinks%20about%20India's%20stand%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20does%2C%20indeed%2C%20matter%20to%20India.%20No%20matter%20what%20the%20virulently%20nationalist%20ecosystem%20clamours%20for%2C%20decoupling%20from%20the%20West%20is%20not%20an%20option%20for%20India.%20It%20is%20not%20merely%20about%20diplomatic%20grandstanding.%20Since%202014%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20been%20making%20diplomatic%20and%20cultural%20gestures%20to%20bolster%20India-EU%20relations.%20There%20have%20been%20increased%20levels%20of%20engagement%20to%20secure%20crucial%20strategic%20and%20economic%20partnerships%20between%20India%20and%20the%20EU%20member%20states.%20While%20India's%20relationship%20with%20Ukraine%20may%20not%20have%20been%20headline-making%20historically%2C%20its%20implications%20have%20not%20been%20any%20less%20significant.%20That%20explains%20why%20India%20has%20consistently%20decried%20Russian%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20visit%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20PM%20Modi%20may%20be%20revealing%20India's%20growing%20transactions%20with%20the%20EU%20member%20states%20for%20its%20defence%20and%20strategic%20needs.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20Russian%20manpower%20and%20machines%20have%20put%20up%20a%20dismal%20performance%20in%20the%20current%20theatre.%20It's%20high%20time%20Indian%20generals%20stopped%20defending%20the%20Russian%20infrastructure%20just%20because%20they%2C%20too%2C%20are%20dependent%20on%20it%20and%20must%20swear%20by%20its%20fierceness.%20India%20has%20options%20for%20its%20defence%20and%20modernisation%20needs%20and%20must%20use%20them.%20After%20all%2C%20what%20use%20are%20partnerships%20like%20the%20Trade%20and%20Technology%20Council%20(TTC)%20that%20the%20EU%20set%20up%20with%20India%20in%20April%202022%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExports%20From%20Russia%20Are%20Dwindling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20brought%20back%20into%20the%20picture%20that%20India's%20arms%20procurement%20from%20Russia%20saw%20a%20significant%20drop%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Russia's%20annexation%20of%20Crimea%20in%202014.%20The%20trend%20has%20been%20continuing%2C%20and%20as%20per%20the%20Stockholm%20International%20Peace%20Research%20Institute's%20latest%20reports%2C%20Russian%20exports%20to%20India%20have%20sharply%20declined%20from%2076%25%20in%202009%E2%80%932013%20to%2036%25%20in%202019-2024.%20While%20India%20remains%20the%20Russian%20arms%20industry's%20biggest%20market%2C%20it's%20also%20shopping%20from%20elsewhere%2C%20and%20that%20cart%20is%20getting%20bigger.%20A%20war-stressed%20Moscow%20is%20unlikely%20to%20meet%20New%20Delhi's%20growing%20defence%20needs%20owing%20to%20the%20latter's%20neighbourhood%20concerns.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAu%20contraire%2C%20other%20countries%20are%20pushing%20their%20catalogues%20for%20New%20Delhi%20to%20browse.%20The%20French%20are%20coming%20hot%20and%20sexy%20with%20their%20Rafael%20jets%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdefence%20industrial%20roadmap%E2%80%9D%20to%20jointly%20design%20and%20develop%20mechanical%20infrastructure.%20India%20and%20France%20have%20joined%20hands%20in%20building%20submarines%2C%20combat%20aircraft%20engines%2C%20and%20multi-role%20helicopters.%20Ukraine%2C%20accounting%20for%2011%25%20of%20India's%20total%20defence%20imports%2C%20too%2C%20is%20an%20important%20partner.%20India%20is%20also%20deepening%20defence%20and%20security%20ties%20with%20countries%20like%20South%20Korea%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20Poland.%20It%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20PM%20Modi%20made%20a%20pit%20stop%20in%20Poland%20before%20heading%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Wise%20Move%20By%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20maintaining%20its%20stance%20of%20strategic%20neutrality%2C%20India%20is%20securing%20self-interest-driven%20allies%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20without%20the%20overlordship%20of%20the%20US.%20It%20is%20a%20wise%20move%20on%20India's%20part%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20ever-looming%20shadow%20of%20China%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20%C2%A0The%20US%20has%20exhibited%20reluctance%20to%20share%20crucial%20defence%20technology%20with%20India%20despite%20promises%20and%20agreements%2C%20like%20the%20one%20between%20General%20Electric%20and%20Indian%20partners%20for%20technology%20to%20power%20the%20new%20fleet%20of%20fighter%20jets.%20India%20knows%20better%20than%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20US%2C%20a%20country%20that%20holds%20its%20military-industrial%20complex%20dearer%20than%20any%20ideological%20principle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20India%E2%80%94while%20being%20on%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20side%20of%20peace%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94is%20keeping%20its%20national%20interests%20above%20everything%20else.%20Mykhailo%20Podolyak%2C%20a%20presidential%20adviser%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20acknowledges%20that%20India%20%E2%80%9Creally%20has%20a%20certain%20influence%E2%80%9D%20over%20Russia.%20It%20is%20this%20reputation%20that%20India%20aims%20to%2C%20ought%20to%20capitalise%20on%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20dependable%20global%20negotiator.%20Only%20those%20who%20have%20power%20can%20negotiate%2C%20the%20rest%20only%20nudge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20for%20Modi's%20Ukraine%20visit%20is%20almost%20perfect.%20India%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20use%20a%20magic%20wand%20to%20bring%20Moscow%20and%20Kyiv%20to%20the%20negotiating%20table.%20The%20military%20situation%20remains%20hot.%20Even%20minor%20dialling%20down%20of%20fighting%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%20will%20be%20enough%20for%20India's%20influence%20optics.%20No%20significant%20developments%20in%20the%20region%20can%20be%20expected%20till%20the%20US%20elects%20its%20next%20president.%20Till%20the%20US%20gets%20its%20house%20in%20order%20and%20views%20its%20NATO%20obligations%20afresh%2C%20the%20window%20is%20open%20for%20India%20to%20pedal%20hard%20towards%20its%20strategic%20goals%E2%80%94choosing%20realism%20over%20idealism%20and%20empty%20talk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724479200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Frodtqa18_modi-ukraine_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-in-ukraine-and-the-realism-we-are-missing-6406652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20maintaining%20its%20stance%20of%20strategic%20neutrality%2C%20India%20is%20securing%20self-interest-driven%20allies%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20without%20the%20overlordship%20of%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-in-ukraine-and-the-realism-we-are-missing-6406652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samantha's%20latest%20look%20sparks%20health%20concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724478706000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112756551%2Cimgsize-20366.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsamantha-ruth-prabhu-sparks-health-concerns-with-her-recent-public-appearance-fans-ask-is-she-fine%2Farticleshow%2F112756551.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112756551.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESamantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%20who%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20'Citadel%3A%20Honey%20Bunny'%2C%20made%20heads%20turn%20when%20she%20attended%20the%20event%20in%20her%20stunning%20black%20crop%20top%20outfit.%20However%2C%20the%20actress%20sparked%20concern%20among%20her%20fans%20with%20her%20noticeable%20'transformation%2C'%20as%20some%20users%20pointed%20out%20her%20recent%20'weight%20loss'%20in%20a%20video%20from%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsamantha-ruth-prabhu-sparks-health-concerns-with-her-recent-public-appearance-fans-ask-is-she-fine%2Farticleshow%2F112756551.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Tough%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Dhawan's%20Honest%20Confession%20On%20Retirement%20Decision%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shikhar%20Dhawan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F737-shikhar-dhawan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShikhar%20Dhawan%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20international%20and%20domestic%20cricket%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20left-handed%20batter%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20post%20a%20video%20message%20where%20he%20announced%20his%20decision%20and%20thanks%20both%20fans%20and%20associations%20for%20their%20love%20and%20support.%20Dhawan%20last%20played%20for%20India%20back%20in%202022%20during%20the%20ODI%20series%20against%20Bangladesh.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fhtcity%2Fht-exclusive-first-interview-shikhar-dhawan-announces-retirement-from-cricket-after-2-decades-it-s-time-now-101724413853982.html%5C%22%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dhawan%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20retire%20and%20said%20that%20although%20it%20was%20not%20tough%20for%20him%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20quite%20emotional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20tough%2C%20but%20it%20is%20emotional%2C%20yes%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20in%20the%20sense%20of%20me%20being%20sad%20about%20it.%20I%20feel%20the%20emotion%20of%20gratitude%20and%20love.%20I%20have%20given%20half%20of%20my%20waking%20life%20to%20cricket%2C%20and%20it's%20time%20now%20to%20retire%2C%20or%20rather%2C%20give%20%E2%80%98vishraam'%20to%20it.%20I'm%20totally%20enjoying%20relaxing%20and%20spending%20time%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhawan%20told%20Hindustan%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhawan%20also%20said%20that%20retirement%20will%20not%20mean%20that%20he%20will%20lose%20his%20fame%20and%20even%20added%20that%20he%20is%20inside%20the%20hearts%20of%20his%20fans%20even%20if%20he%20is%20not%20playing%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20will%20I%20lose%20fame%20if%20I%20give%20up%20cricket%3F%20Who%20knows%2C%20the%20fame%20might%20increase%20also.%20Main%20logon%20ke%20dilon%20mein%20basa%20hua%20hoon.%20Not%20only%20through%20cricket%E2%80%A6sometimes%20even%20through%20my%20Instagram%20reels%20(laughs).%20I'm%20definite%20that%20the%20love%20I%20get%20from%20people%20will%20continue%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20product%20of%20Sonnet%20Club%20and%20a%20fighter%20from%20West%20Delhi%2C%C2%A0Dhawan%C2%A0appeared%20in%2034%20Tests%2C%20167%20ODIs%20and%2068%20T20Is%20for%20India%20but%20had%20fallen%20out%20of%20favour%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20due%20to%20patchy%20form%20and%20emergence%20of%20younger%20opening%20talents%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20best%20came%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20in%20which%20he%20amassed%206793%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2044.11%2C%20including%2017%20hundreds%20and%2039%20fifties.%20He%20averaged%2040.61%20for%20his%202315%20Test%20runs%2C%20which%20featured%20seven%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724478540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fk30qedco_shikhar-dhawan_625x300_24_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-tough-but-shikhar-dhawans-honest-confession-on-retirement-decision-6406611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shikhar%20Dhawan%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20international%20and%20domestic%20cricket%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-tough-but-shikhar-dhawans-honest-confession-on-retirement-decision-6406611%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi's%20