2C%20with%20HYDRA%20officials%20arriving%20on-site%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20contingent%20of%20police%20personnel%20to%20ensure%20the%20process%20proceeded%20without%20interruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724477880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fprtfm4tg_nagarjuna-n-convention-centre-_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbulldozer-action-on-actor-nagarjunas-n-convention-centre-in-hyderabad-6406442%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hyderabad%20Disaster%20Response%20and%20Assets%20Monitoring%20and%20Protection%20(HYDRA)%20authorities%20have%20begun%20demolishing%20the%20N-Convention%20Centre%2C%20a%20sprawling%20establishment%20owned%20by%20prominent%20actor%20Nagarjuna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbulldozer-action-on-actor-nagarjunas-n-convention-centre-in-hyderabad-6406442%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inspired%20By%20'Drishyam'%2C%20Ex%20Cop%20Kills%20Noida%20Businessman%20Over%20Property%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Delhi%20Police%20constable%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20killing%20a%20Greater%20Noida-based%20businessman%20to%20take%20possession%20of%20his%20flat.%20The%20accused%2C%20Praveen%2C%2042%2C%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20late%20Thursday%2C%2013%20days%20after%20businessman%20Ankush%20Sharma%20was%20reported%20missing%20by%20his%20family.%20The%20former%20constable%20allegedly%20planned%20the%20murder%20in%20a%20week%20after%20watching%20Ajay%20Devgn%20and%20Tabu's%20crime-thriller%2C%20%3Cem%3EDrishyam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20other%20crime%20web%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Praveen%20first%20met%20Mr%20Sharma%20through%20someone.%20The%20businessman%20wanted%20to%20sell%20his%20flat%20in%20a%20Greater%20Noida%20society%2C%20said%20Saad%20Miya%20Khan%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%2C%20Greater%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20fixed%20the%20deal%20for%20%E2%82%B91.20%20crore.%20Praveen%20gave%20Sharma%20%E2%82%B98%20lakh%20and%20the%20transfer%20memorandum%20process%20was%20initiated%20between%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20started%20after%20Ankush%20Sharma%20found%20that%20the%20price%20of%20the%20flat%2C%20in%20SKA%20society%2C%20was%20more%20than%20what%20the%20two%20parties%20had%20agreed%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnhappy%2C%20Mr%20Praveen%20hatched%20a%20plan%20to%20kill%20Ankush%20Sharma.%20On%20August%209%2C%20he%20picked%20Mr%20Sharma%20up%20from%20his%20office%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20give%20him%20money%20for%20the%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20later%20reached%20a%20society's%20parking%20where%20the%20two%20started%20drinking.%20When%20Ankush%20Sharma%20got%20drunk%2C%20Mr%20Praveen%20hit%20him%20with%20a%20hammer%20on%20the%20head%20before%20strangling%20him%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20August%209%2C%20Mr%20Praveen%20hid%20the%20body%20on%20a%20disputed%20property%20not%20visited%20often%20by%20anyone%2C%20the%20senior%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20family%20lodged%20a%20missing%20complaint%20at%20the%20Beta-2%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20police%20looked%20into%20more%20than%20100%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20intelligence%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Mr%20Praveen.%20He%20also%20informed%20the%20police%20where%20he%20hid%20the%20victim's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20recovered%20the%20hammer%20used%20in%20the%20crime%20and%20a%20car%20from%20the%20accused%2C%20Khan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Praveen%20has%20been%20booked%20under%20Sections%20103(1)%20(charges%20of%20murder)%2C%20238%20(destroying%20evidence)%20and%20123%20(giving%20poison%20to%20another%20person)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20roughly%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Chhattisgarh%20woman%20was%20reported.%20The%2028-year-old%20was%20allegedly%20killed%20and%20her%20body%20was%20buried%20by%20her%20estranged%20husband%20and%20paramour.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20two%20men%20also%20watched%20%3Cem%3EDrishyam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20taking%20cues%20to%20hide%20the%20body%20and%20avoid%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20July%2019%20and%20the%20police%20arrested%20the%20two%20accused%20--%20Lukesh%20Sahu%20(29)%2C%20the%20woman's%20estranged%20husband%2C%20and%20Raja%20Ram%20Sahu%20(26)%20with%20whom%20she%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724477820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-07%2F1po0gju8_noida-police-generic-_625x300_23_July_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-constable-takes-cue-from-drishyam-murders-greater-noida-based-businessman-6406450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20Delhi%20Police%20constable%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20killing%20a%20Greater%20Noida-based%20businessman%20to%20take%20possession%20of%20his%20flat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-constable-takes-cue-from-drishyam-murders-greater-noida-based-businessman-6406450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himanshi's%20cryptic%20post%20an%20indirect%20dig%20at%20Asim%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724477132000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112756003%2Cimgsize-48854.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpunjabi%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fhimanshi-khuranas-cryptic-posts-about-asim-riaz%2Farticleshow%2F112755611.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22