20to%20almost%20C%241.2%20million%20(%24888%2C000)%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMason%20and%20Ahn%20are%20each%20suing%20RBC%20for%20wrongful%20dismissal.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20Mr.%20Mason's%20knowledge%2C%20and%20at%20his%20urging%2C%20Ms.%20Ahn%20misused%20her%20power%20as%20CFO%20to%20bestow%20significant%20compensation%20increases%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20an%20executive-level%20promotion%20upon%20Mr.%20Mason%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20'Project%20Ken'%20the%20two%20were%20pursuing%20together%20while%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20close%20personal%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said%20in%20its%20latest%20court%20filing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week%20ago%2C%20the%20bank%20made%20similar%20claims%20against%20Ahn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Mason%20and%20Ahn%20did%20not%20immediately%20reply%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20Friday%20afternoon.%20In%20their%20lawsuits%2C%20they%20said%20they%20did%20not%20have%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20and%20were%20just%20friends.%20Ahn%20said%20the%20bank%20subjected%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bpalpable%20reputational%20harm%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20humiliation%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20fired%20her.%20Mason%20has%20said%20the%20bank%20would%20not%20have%20handled%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20same%20fashion%20if%20the%20two%20were%20both%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20RBC%20declined%20to%20comment%20and%20referred%20back%20to%20its%20earlier%20statements%20on%20the%20cases.%20The%20bank%20has%20previously%20said%20it%20hired%20external%20legal%20counsel%20to%20conduct%20an%20investigation%20after%20receiving%20an%20anonymous%20complaint%20in%20March%20that%20Ahn%20and%20Mason%20had%20been%20seen%20together%20and%20were%20having%20a%20relationship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompensation%20Increases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20alleges%20that%20Mason's%20total%20compensation%20for%20fiscal%202023%20w