%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamala%20Harris%20Gears%20Up%20For%20Polls%2C%20Mallika%20Sherawat's%202009%20Prediction%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Mallika%20Sherawat%20applauded%20US%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20on%20her%20'self-made'%20political%20career%20after%20she%20was%20named%20as%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20official%20candidate%20for%20the%20US%20Presidential%20elections.%20%26quot%3BComing%20from%20India%2C%20female%20politicians%20are%20so%20rare.%20If%20they%20are%20there%2C%20they%20come%20from%20a%20very%20dynastic%20or%20royal%20family.%20Here%20I%20was%20meeting%20a%20lady%20who%20had%20built%20everything%20with%20her%20own%20two%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20Sherawat%20told%20Vanity%20Fair%20in%20an%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Welcome'%20actor%20had%20incidentally%20hinted%20in%202009%20that%20Kamala%20Harris%20could%20go%20on%20to%20become%20the%20US%20President%2C%20a%20post%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20fun%20at%20a%20fancy%20event%20with%20a%20woman%20who%20they%20say%20could%20be%20US%20President%2C%20Kamala%20Harris.%20Chicks%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20Sherawat%20had%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20in%202009.%20It%20was%20a%20prescient%20remark%2C%20made%20well%20before%20Harris%2C%20then%20a%20San%20Francisco%20attorney%2C%20became%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominee.%20Her%20resurfaced%20tweet%20has%20sparked%20a%20buzz%20on%20social%20media%20with%20some%20people%20calling%20Mallika%20Sherawat%20a%20clairvoyant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHaving%20fun%20at%20a%20fancy%20event%20with%20a%20woman%20who%20they%20say%20could%20be%20US%20President%2C%20Kamala%20Harris.%20Chicks%20rule!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallika%20Sherawat%20(%40mallikasherawat)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmallikasherawat%2Fstatus%2F2288254299%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2023%2C%202009%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20took%20place%20when%20Sherawat%20was%20playing%20a%20character%20inspired%20by%20Harris%20in%20an%20indie%20film%20'Politics%20of%20Love'%20(2011).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESherawat%2C%20who%20attended%20a%20Beverly%20Hills%20fundraiser%20for%20Harris%20in%202009%2C%20recalled%20feeling%20out%20of%20place%20at%20the%20event.%20She%20said%20Harris%20made%20her%20feel%20comfortable%2C%20advising%20her%20to%20get%20out%20of%20her%20comfort%20zone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20feeling%20like%20a%20fish%20out%20of%20water.%20It%20was%20my%20first%20time%20in%20LA%2C%20and%20she%20really%20put%20me%20at%20ease.%20I%20remember%20her%20saying%20that%20getting%20out%20of%20your%20comfort%20zone%20is%20good%20to%20build%20character%20and%20it%20will%20make%20you%20a%20stronger%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20follow%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2Fstory%2Fkamala-harris-inspired-a-character-in-a-movie-youll-probably-never-see-politics-of-love%5C%22%3EVanity%20Fair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20want%20of%20a%20better%20term%2C%20she%20was%20like%20one%20of%20us-a%20normal%20person%20with%20inspiring%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2047-year-old%20actor%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20is%20now%20the%20Democratic%20Presidential%20candidate%20for%20the%20November%202024%20US%20elections%2C%20following%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20race%20last%20month.%20This%20development%20has%20led%20to%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20becoming%20the%20oldest%20candidate%20in%20the%20race%2C%20and%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20series%20of%20personal%20attacks%20on%20Harris%20from%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallika%20Sherawat%20has%20worked%20in%20several%20movies%20which%20hit%20commercial%20success%20in%20Bollywood.%20Her%20first%20hit%20was%20Anurag%20Basu's%20'Murder'%20(2004).%20She%20was%20also%20seen%20in%20popular%20Bollywood%20hits%20such%20as%20'Pyarr%20Ke%20Side%20Effects'%20(2006)%2C%20'Welcome'%20(2007)%2C%20and%20'Guru'%20(2007).%20She%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20a%202021%20comedy-drama%20'RK%2FRKay'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20film%20'Politics%20of%20Love'%20(2011)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20producers%20Govind%20Menon%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20the%20Democrat-Republican%20divide%20wasn't%20as%20toxic%20and%20as%20horrible%20as%20it%20is%20now.%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20we%20would've%20made%20that%20movie%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallika%20Sherawat%20played%20the%20character%20of%20a%20campaign%20worker%20for%20Barrack%20Obama%20in%20the%20film.%20This%20character%20was%20inspired%20by%20Kamala%20Harris%20serving%20as%20an%20interesting%20footnote%20in%20the%20trajectory%20of%20her%20political%20career%20from%20being%20a%20district%20attorney%20to%20vouching%20for%20a%20'new%20America'%20while%20accepting%20the%20presidential%20nominee%20at%20the%20Democratic%20Convention%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallika%20Sherawat%20also%20recalls%20%26quot%3Bcasually%20asking%26quot%3B%20of%20Harris%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20think%2C%20Kamala%2C%20you%20could%20be%20president%20one%20day%3F%26quot%3B%20To%20which%20Harris%20had%20confidently%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20not%3F%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0If%20she%20wins%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20not%20only%20make%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20woman%20US%20President%20but%20also%20the%20first%20black%20woman%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724474580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fulk4pmj8_kamala-harris-mallika-sherawat-_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkamala-harris-gears-up-for-polls-mallika-sherawats-2009-prediction-viral-6406283%2