y%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-why-cbi-wants-lie-detector-test-for-kolkata-rape-murder-victims-colleagues-6401012%5C%22%3Efound%20a%20Bluetooth%20earphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20crime%20scene%20during%20initial%20investigation%20after%20the%20body%20of%20the%20woman%20was%20found%20inside%20the%20seminar%20hall%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCTV%20footage%20shows%20Sanjay%20Roy%20entering%20the%20hospital%20at%201.03%20am%2C%20sources%20said.%20During%20interrogation%2C%20the%20police%20had%20shown%20him%20the%20CCTV%20evidence%2C%20after%20which%20Sanjay%20Roy%20admitted%20to%20the%20crime%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20reached%20the%20hospital%20at%201.03%20am%20the%20night%20the%20junior%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%2C%20Sanjay%20Roy%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkey-suspect-sanjay-roy-in-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-case-went-to-red-light-area-cops-6380576%5C%22%3Egone%20to%20two%20brothels%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20the%20police%20have%20said.%20He%20went%20to%20the%20red%20light%20area%20Sonagachi%20on%20August%208%20night%2C%20drank%20alcohol%2C%20and%20visited%20two%20brothels%20one%20after%20another%2C%20sources%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20midnight.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20he%20was%20seen%20on%20CCTV%20entering%20and%20leaving%20the%20seminar%20hall%2C%20where%20the%20junior%20doctor%20had%20gone%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20sparked%20protests%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20protests%20have%20been%20especially%20intense%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20special%20court%20in%20Kolkata%20yesterday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkey-suspect-sanjay-roy-in-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-case-went-to-red-light-area-cops-6380