%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-10-1724336056-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362636%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMedini%20Homestay%20is%20a%20green%20oasis%20where%20fruit%2C%20herb%20and%20vegetable%20trees%20thrive%20together%20in%20a%20single%20space.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20took%20on%20the%20challenge%20head-on.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20land%20had%20been%20excavated%20in%20parts%2C%20thus%20lacking%20a%20topsoil%20layer.%20When%20I%20began%20work%20on%20the%20land%2C%20there%20were%20around%20three%20trees%20and%20a%20small%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356551%2Fbest-tea-plantation-estates-homestays-legacy-heritage-india-assam-tamil-nadu-darjeeling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatch%20of%20tea%20plantation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20attempted%20by%20the%20previous%20owner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20today%2C%20when%20guests%20compliment%20the%20land%20thriving%20in%20all%20its%20green%20glory%2C%20they%20are%20compelled%20to%20wonder%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20kept%20planting%20and%20learning%20as%20we%20went%20along%2C%E2%80%9D%20Deka%20answers.%20He%20recounts%20one%20instance%20that%20baffled%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20putting%20green%20manure%20on%20the%20land%20but%20not%20seeing%20results.%20An%20elderly%20man%20who%20was%20on%20the%20land%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20asked%20me%20to%20%E2%80%98throw%20some%20urea%E2%80%99%20and%20said%20that%20would%20make%20the%20land%20flourish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20hear%20someone%20so%20experienced%20advising%20me%20to%20use%20chemicals.%20It%20became%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20the%20ideas%20of%20even%20seasoned%20people%20had%20been%20changed%20by%20industrial%20farming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20