through%20its%20products.%20%E2%80%98Marwadi%20Manwar%E2%80%99%20is%20taking%20the%20authentic%20flavours%20of%20Rajasthan%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20and%20beyond%20with%20their%20delicious%20homemade%20pickles%2C%20papads%2C%20and%20other%20traditional%20delicacies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20business%20is%20touching%20new%20heights%20by%20the%20day%2C%20we%20have%20a%20catch%20here.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20Marwadi%20Manwar%20is%20Nirmala%20Shekhawat%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F237078%2Fassam-woman-entrepreneur-small-biz-pickles-homemade-homemaker-business-at-home-ang136%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20woman%20who%20rose%20like%20a%20phoenix%20from%20the%20ashes%20of%20personal%20loss.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20happy%20family%2C%20comprising%20herself%2C%20her%20husband%20Karan%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20and%20their%20three%20children%2C%20everything%20seemed%20to%20be%20going%20well%20for%20Nirmala%2C%20until%201%20February%2C%202020%2C%20when%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20a%20brain%20haemorrhage.%20As%20if%20this%20tragedy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20that%20followed%20brought%20financial%20struggles%2C%20adding%20to%20Nirmala%E2%80%99s%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC-xHu0nyk4g%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC-xHu0nyk4g%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%