me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20putting%20me%20off%2C%20this%20disclaimer%20has%20me%20intrigued.%20I%20am%20finally%20about%20to%20discover%20the%20journey%20of%20this%20visually%20impaired%20stalwart%20in%20starting%20a%20trust%20that%20has%20bettered%20the%20lives%20of%20over%20500%20senior%20citizens%20in%20the%20Kachchh%20region%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20has%20been%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20disabled%20individuals%20in%20the%20state%2C%20particularly%20for%20abandoned%20visually%20impaired%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335260%2Fshantanu-naidu-startup-the-goodfellows-helps-senior-citizens-connect-with-youth-ratan-tata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Left%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves%20by%20their%20families%2C%20these%20elderly%20individuals%20find%20comfort%20in%20Laljibhai%E2%80%99s%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20takes%20great%20pride%20in%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20reveals%2C%20it%20all%20started%20when%20he%20was%2017%20years%20old.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20eyes%20were%20affected%20by%20glaucoma%20and%20I%20lost%20my%20vision.%20It%20was%20almost%20like%20I%20went%20to%20bed%20one%20night%20and%20woke%20up%20blind%20the%20next%20day.%20My%20life%20changed%20completely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrapped%20in%20the%20four%20walls%20of%20his%20home%20with%20only%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20visits%20to%20look%20forward%20to%2C%20Laljibhai%20felt%20he%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20proverbial%20tunnel%20%E2%80%94%20one%20without%20a%20light%20at%20the%20end.%20Losing%20his%20eyesight%20had%20done%20more%20than%20fluster%20him%3B%20it%20had%20also%20threatened%20to%20put%20a%20stopper%20on%20his%20career%20goals.%20He%20could%20no%20longer%20hope%20to%20study%20at%20the%20universities%20he%20was%20looking%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Bhachau%20(a%20city%20under%2