%20if%20I%20were%20in%20a%20permanent%20lockdown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20with%20disabilities%20are%20forced%20to%20stay%20indoors%20because%20of%20such%20infrastructural%20barriers.%20The%20World%20Bank%20reports%20that%20about%2015%25%20of%20the%20global%20population%20has%20some%20form%20of%20disability.%20Given%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20of%20over%201.4%20billion%2C%20this%20translates%20to%20approximately%2021%20crore%20people%20with%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20the%20question%3A%20Where%20are%20these%20individuals%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disabled%20community%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20often%20unseen%20and%20confined%20to%20their%20homes.%20An%20important%20question%20to%20consider%20then%20is%20what%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20about%20accessibility.%20The%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20(RPwD)%20Act%20of%202016%20mandates%20equal%20access%20and%20universal%20design%20standards%2C%20but%20enforcement%20is%20often%20inadequate%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20projects%20often%20feature%20substandard%20accessibility%20features%2C%20with%20ramps%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20meet%20necessary%20standards.%20There%20is%20a%20notable%20lack%20of%20action%20from%20startups%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20wheelchair%20advocates%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20remarks.%20To%20fill%20this%20gap%2C%20he%20created%20RampMyCity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRampMyCity%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20created%20just%20from%20my%20ideas%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20grew%20out%20of%20my%20real-life%20experiences.%20We%20visit%20each%20location%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20ramp%20requirements%20and%20then%20devise%20a%20solution%20that%20works%20without%20disrupting%20the%20current%20setup.%20Our%20approach%20is%20always%20practical%20and%20starts%20from%20the%20bottom%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20c