0%9D%20he%20reveals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20laws%20have%20defined%20ramp%20standards%2C%20the%20existing%20infrastructure%20often%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20these%20standards%20due%20to%20space%20constraints%20and%20obstacles%20like%20parking%20and%20drainage.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20conduct%20a%20technical%20audit%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20type%20of%20ramp%20for%20each%20location%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20ramp%20is%20customised%20to%20fit%20the%20site%E2%80%99s%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ipsita%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20has%20known%20Prateek%20since%20college%20and%20has%20worked%20with%20RampMyCity%20since%202018%2C%20the%20key%20to%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20Prateek%E2%80%99s%20drive%20to%20motivate%20himself%20and%20those%20around%20him.%20She%20describes%20how%20they%20started%20by%20inviting%20wheelchair%20users%20to%20events%20to%20help%20them%20break%20out%20of%20their%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turning%20point%20for%20Prateek%20came%20in%202022%20when%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20took%20notice%20of%20his%20work%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20install%20ramps%20at%2010%20prominent%20government%20buildings%20in%20Bengaluru.%20The%20startup%20successfully%20installed%20ramps%20in%20a%20park%2C%20a%20hospital%2C%20and%20at%20other%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20Dunzo%20sponsoring%20the%20initiative%2C%20they%20added%2010%20ramps%20in%20just%2020%20days.%20That%20moment%20marked%20a%20new%20chapter%20for%20us%20and%20gave%20us%20the%20visibility%20we%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20ramped%20Church%20Street%2C%20over%20100%20restaurants%2C%2050%2B%20police%20stations%2C%20malls%2C%20and%20ATMs%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wheelchair-friendly%20cities%20in%20India.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-23_11zon-1723819163-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20ramped%20Church%20Street%2C%20over%20100%20restaurants%2C%2050%2B%20police%20stations%2C%20malls%2C%20and%20ATMs%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20most%20wheelchair-friendly%20cities%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20RampMyCity%20has%20expanded%20to%20various%20cities%2C%20including%20Delhi%2C%20Cyber%20Hub%2C%20Galleria%20Market%20in%20Goa%2C%20and%20popular%20markets%20in%20Mumbai.%20Currently%2C%20it%20is%20working%20on%20ramping%20up%20police%20stations%20and%20eateries%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERampMyCity%20handles%20everything%20%E2%80%93%20from%20ramps%20and%20railings%20to%20furniture%20and%20bathroom%20accessories%2C%20elevators%2C%20wheelchairs%2C%20and%20emergency%20evacuation%20solutions.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20team%20provides%20special%20wheelchairs%20that%20can%20navigate%20stairs%20during%20emergencies%20when%20elevators%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20used.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sources%20these%20products%20from%20across%20India%2C%20both%20locally%20and%20centrally%2C%20to%20meet%20various%20needs.%20Through%20this%2C%20it%20has%20reinvigorated%20the%20industry%2C%20increasing%20supply%20and%20opening%20the%20market%20to%20new%20players%20focused%20on%20disability%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20been%20asked%20by%20numerous%20organisations%20to%20create%20end-to-end%20accessibility%20solutions%20for%20their%20workplaces%2C%20which%20include%20everything%20from%20accessible%20parking%20and%20entry%20routes%20to%20doors%20and%20charging%20points.%20We%20also%20address%20how%20workspaces%2C%20card-punch%20areas%2C%20washrooms%2C%20and%20canteens%20are%20all%20designed%20to%20be%20inclusive%20and%20user-friendly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20talks%20about%20how%20India%20will%20be%20developed%20by%202047%2C%20but%20we%20must%20remember%20that%20true%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F216171%2Fips-hero-west-bengal-differently-abled-friendly-police-stations-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20starts%20with%20accessibility%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20shares%2C%20while%20remarking%20that%20countries%20like%20Singapore%20and%20those%20in%20Europe%20are%20considered%20developed%20because%20they%20are%20accessible.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20India%20to%20reach%20that%20level%2C%20accessibility%20must%20come%20first.%20This%20is%20the%20vision%20we%20strive%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETapping%20into%20the%20corporate%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reality%20is%20that%20many%20people%20have%20limited%20budgets%20for%20accessibility%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Prateek.%20Cafes%20might%20only%20spend%20a%20few%20thousand%20on%20ramps%2C%20but%20proper%20ramps%20with%20the%20right%20length%20and%20gradient%20cost%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20challenge%20for%20Prateek%20and%20his%20team%20because%20people%20wanted%20ramps%20but%20weren%E2%80%99t%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20scale%20up%20quickly%2C%20aiming%20for%20thousands%20of%20ramps%20per%20year%2C%20not%20just%20dozens.%20Even%20large%20corporations%20with%20substantial%20revenues%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20budget%20for%20true%20accessibility.%20We%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20in%20CSR%20and%20philanthropic%20funding%20to%20help%20us%20grow%20and%20meet%20our%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%2070%25%20of%20the%20total%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20spending%20from%202018%20through%202021%20went%20to%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20rural%20development%2C%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20and%20poverty%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20report.%20RampMyCity%20approached%20these%20corporations%2C%20proposing%20they%20invest%20in%20public%20accessibility%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offered%20to%20manage%20installations%20in%20public%20places%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20police%20stations%2C%20with%20the%20government%20providing%20the%20necessary%20permissions.%20This%20model%20has%20helped%20RampMyCity%20scale%20rapidly%2C%20shares%20Prateek%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20startup%20is%20currently%20working%20to%20tap%20into%20this%20large%20pool%20of%20CSR%20money%20to%20improve%20public%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20he%20stayed%20motivated%20during%20the%20early%20days%20of%20his%20startup%20while%20adjusting%20to%20life%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20an%20unclear%20path%20ahead%2C%20Prateek%20says%20it%20was%20all%20about%20taking%20baby%20steps.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20are%20consistent%20in%20working%20towards%20your%20goals%2C%20there%20will%20always%20be%20a%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20quoting%20his%20personal%20mantra%3A%20%3Cem%3EKismat%20ke%20bharose%20mat%20baithiye%3B%20kismat%20khud%20aapke%20bharose%20baithi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20luck%2Fkismet%3B%20it%20is%20waiting%20for%20you%20to%20make%20a%20move).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20injury%20forced%20me%20to%20face%20myself.%20I%20could%20either%20become%20my%20greatest%20ally%20or%20my%20biggest%20enemy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Years%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20when%20Prateek%20reviewed%20his%20life%2C%20his%20past%20achievements%2C%20and%20took%20note%20of%20the%20go-getting%20attitude%20he%20had%20always%20had%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20piece%20together%20his%20identity.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288588%2Fbrittle-bone-disease-didnt-stop-kerala-doctor-fathima-asla-inspiration%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewed%20focus%20on%20his%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20facing%20similar%20struggles%2C%20his%20advice%20is%20to%20trust%20the%20process.%20%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20you%20will%20see%20how%20the%20bigger%20plan%20was%20made%20for%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20never%20regretted%20my%20injury%20or%20my%20life%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%20Instead%2C%20I%20see%20it%20as%20an%20amazing%20opportunity%20that%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20had%20otherwise.%20It%E2%80%99s%20allowed%20me%20to%20see%20how%20many%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20live%20full%2C%20normal%20lives%3B%20travel%2C%20work%2C%20and%20be%20part%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Pictures%20Courtesy%3A%20Prateek%20Khandelwal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Fglobalassets%2Fnoindex%2F2022%2Fbain_report_india_philanthropy_report-2022.pdf%5C%22%3Ehttp