s%20the%20English%20Channel%E2%80%99%3A%20New%20Mom%E2%80%99s%20Search%20for%20Self-Love%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20life%20I%20was%20living%20was%20not%20enough%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi%20Deore%2C%20a%20quintessential%20water%20baby.%20As%20a%20toddler%2C%20whenever%20she%20was%20upset%20or%20cranky%2C%20her%20parents%20would%20pacify%20her%20by%20placing%20her%20in%20a%20tub%20of%20water%20or%20giving%20her%20some%20water%20to%20play%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20grew%2C%20Tanvi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359081%2Franjita-gogoi-assam-swimming-athlete-senior-citizen-champion-international-armwrestling-powerlifting-competition%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20for%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E%20blossomed%2C%20and%20she%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20a%20pool%20in%20Nashik%2C%20both%20before%20and%20after%20school.%20Her%20dedication%20led%20her%20to%20become%20a%20champion%20swimmer%20at%20the%20school%20and%20district%20levels.%20However%2C%20after%20Class%209%2C%20swimming%20took%20a%20backseat%20as%20her%20studies%20became%20the%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%2018%20years%2C%20education%2C%20business%2C%20marriage%2C%20and%20raising%20kids%20took%20precedence%2C%20and%20her%20sport%20faded%20into%20the%20background.%20As%20a%20young%20mother%2C%20she%20juggled%20these%20roles%20while%20longing%20for%20the%20determined%20young%20girl%20who%20once%20embraced%20every%20challenge.%20The%20demands%20of%20everyday%20life%20%E2%80%94%20managing%20a%20resort%20in%20Nashik%2C%20and%20being%20a%20mother%2C%20wife%2C%20and%20daughter%20%E2%80%94%20began%20to%20take%20their%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20she%20lost%20herself%2C%20along%20with%20the%20fearless%20young%20girl%20who%20was%20up%20for%20any%20challenge%2C%20she%20wondered%3F%20This%20search%20for%20self-love%20led%20her%20back%20to%20her%20first%20love%3A%20