%20Channel%20swim%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20coach%20Srikaanth%20Viswanathan%2C%20an%20accomplished%20open-water%20swimmer%20who%20had%20completed%20the%20triple%20crown%20of%20open-water%20swimming.%20Her%20practice%20sessions%20started%20at%204%20am%2C%20requiring%20her%20to%20wake%20up%20at%203%20am.%20The%20sudden%20shift%20in%20routine%20was%20challenging%2C%20especially%20with%20three-year-old%20twins.%20It%20was%20a%20rollercoaster%20ride%2C%20she%20admits%2C%20involving%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20of%20her%20lifestyle%20and%20schedule.%20Her%20children%20were%20too%20young%20to%20grasp%20the%20magnitude%20of%20what%20their%20mother%20was%20attempting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201071px)%20100vw%2C%201071px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20with%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader%2C%20her%20father.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119.jpeg%201071w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119-500x498.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119-150x149.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119-768x764.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-with-dad-min-1723815119-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361698%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanvi%20with%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader%2C%20her%20father.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20faced%20battles%20both%20physical%20and%20mental.%20In%20the%20early%20days%2C%20she%20struggled%20to%20swim%20for%20more%20than%2020%20minutes%20at%20a%20time.%20She%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20accept%20her%20body%20and%20even%20to%20wear%20a%20swimsuit%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20tired%20very%20easily.%20I%20was%20feeling%20guilty%20about%20leaving%20my%20children.%20As%20I%20dealt%20with%20physical%20acceptance%20and%20mental%20challenges%2C%20my%20coach%20was%20very%20supportive.%20My%20mother%20too%20urged%20me%20to%20follow%20my%20dreams%2C%20as%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20follow%20hers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20gradually%20progressed%20from%20swimming%20for%20just%2020%20minutes%20to%20swimming%20for%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20in%20the%20pool.%20Later%2C%20she%20began%20practising%20in%20open%20water%2C%20training%20in%20the%20dams%20around%20Nashik%20over%20the%20weekends.%20Although%20she%20was%20slowly%20overcoming%20her%20physical%20challenges%2C%20she%20struggled%20to%20achieve%20the%20necessary%20speed%20for%20a%20100-metre%20lap%20during%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20was%20holding%20her%20back%20%E2%80%94%20her%20father%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20given%20her%20his%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKiran%20Chavan%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20his%20daughter%20wanted%20to%20put%20herself%20through%20such%20a%20demanding%20ordeal.%20He%20was%20apprehensive%2C%20knowing%20of%20people%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%20attempting%20this%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20her%20to%20put%20herself%20in%20a%20life-threatening%20position.%20She%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20her%20business%2C%20as%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Why%20put%20your%20life%20at%20risk%3F%20I%20wanted%20to%20protect%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tanvi%20was%20determined%20and%20persuasive.%20When%20letters%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20she%20asked%20her%20coach%20to%20convince%20her%20father.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20her%20coach%20met%20me%20and%20assured%20me%20that%20there%20was%20no%20risk%20of%20life%20and%20she%20would%20be%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20it%20convinced%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMagically%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20required%20timing%20the%20next%20day%20and%20since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20She%20slowly%20gained%20her%20confidence%20back%20and%20started%20practice%20in%20earnest%20for%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20big%20challenge%20to%20tackle%20was%20the%20cold%20conditions%20of%20the%20English%20Channel.%20To%20get%20acclimatised%20to%20cold%20water%2C%20Tanvi%20first%20started%20taking%20only%20cold%20showers.%20She%20also%20started%20sitting%20in%20ice%20baths%20for%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20later%20increased%20to%20one%20hour.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20sit%20in%20ice%20water%20from%202%20am%20to%203%20am%20to%20get%20used%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20found%20happiness%20in%20swimming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-49-1723815126-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%